22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMikaella%20and%20Brandt%20on%20their%20boat%20in%20the%20Pacific.%20%3Cp%3EKyle%20Buckley.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMikaella%20Taylor%2C%2025%2C%20and%20her%20fianc%C3%A9%20moved%20onto%20their%2030-foot%20sailboat%20a%20year%20ago.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ETaylor%20loves%20being%20close%20to%20nature%2C%20living%20a%20more%20minimalist%20lifestyle%2C%20and%20saving%20on%20rent.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt's%20much%20easier%20than%20she%20thought%20it%20would%20be%2C%20and%20she%20plans%20to%20continue%20living%20there%20for%20years.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Mikaella%20Taylor%2C%2025%2C%20a%20small-business%20owner%2C%20who%20moved%20onto%20a%2030-foot%20sailboat%20with%20her%20fianc%C3%A9%20a%20year%20ago.%20The%20conversation%20was%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20fianc%C3%A9%2C%20Brandt%2C%20bought%20our%2030-foot%20sailboat%20six%20years%20ago%20with%20the%20goal%20of%20living%20on%20it.%20That%20was%20before%20I%20met%20him.%20He%20paid%20%249%2C000%20for%20the%20boat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrandt%20studied%20songwriting%20in%20college%2C%20and%20didn't%20know%20much%20about%20boating.%20But%20on%20a%20whim%2C%20he%20went%20on%20a%20sailing%20trip%20in%20the%20Grenadine%20islands.%20He%20fell%20in%20love%20with%20it.%20He%20had%20always%20wanted%20to%20do%20van%20life%2C%20or%20convert%20an%20RV%2C%20and%20when%20he%20realized%20he%20could%20do%20the%20same%20thing%20on%20a%20boat%2C%20he%20wanted%20to%20make%20it%20happen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20we%20got%20to%20the%20point%20in%20our%20relationship%20that%20we%20were%20about%20to%20be%20engaged%20and%20the%20lease%20was%20up%20on%20his%20apartment.%20I%20was%20ready%20to%20move%20out%20of%20where%20I%20was.%20We%20both%20were%20looking%20to%20move%20somewhere%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20we%20went%20through%20the%20process%20of%20getting%20a%20living%20permit%20for%20the%20boat%2C%20which%20requires%20an%20inspection%20by%20the%20harbormaster.%20He%20comes%20to%20inspect%20the%20boat%20for%20safety%2C%20to%20make%20sure%20we're%20going%20to%20keep%20the%20marina%20clean%2C%20and%20that%20we%20can%20move%20the%20boat%20if%20we%20need%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20such%20a%20quick%20and%20easy%20process.%20We%20were%20nervous.%20It%20was%20one%20of%20those%20things%20that%20we%20were%20expecting%20to%20be%20a%20lot%20harder%20than%20it%20was.%20It%20kind%20of%20just%20fell%20into%20our%20lap.%20We%20got%20really%20lucky.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22983%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mikaella%20and%20Brandt%20on%20their%20houseboat%20in%20Southern%20California%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64ee523726dda200194d4938%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22737%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMikaella%20and%20Brandt%20on%20their%20boat.%20%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Mikaella%20Taylor%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EOur%20monthly%20housing%20expense%20is%20an%20%24820%20slip%20fee%20that%20we%20split%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20always%20say%20we%20have%20the%20cheapest%20waterfront%20property%20around.%20We%20pay%20%24820%20for%20our%20slip%20fee%2C%20which%20includes%20fresh%20water%2C%20WiFi%2C%20and%20electricity%20%E2%80%94%20all%20the%20things%20we%20need.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20living%20at%20home%20before%20we%20moved%20on%20the%20boat%20and%20Brandt%20was%20in%20an%20apartment.%20He%20shared%20a%20space%20with%20somebody%2C%20and%20his%20portion%20of%20the%20rent%20was%20around%20%241%2C100%20a%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20talk%20about%20this%2C%20I%20always%20try%20to%20emphasize%20that%20we%20weren't%20just%20moving%20on%20to%20the%20boat%20for%20the%20affordability.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20wanted%20to%20live%20on%20the%20boat%20regardless.%20And%2C%20actually%2C%20we%20were%20prepared%20to%20have%20to%20start%20taking%20on%20another%20job%20if%20it%20meant%20that%20living%20on%20the%20boat%20was%20going%20to%20be%20more%20expensive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20we%20found%20out%20we%20were%20also%20going%20to%20be%20saving%20a%20lot%20of%20money%20by%20doing%20this%2C%20we%20thought%20it%20would%20be%20stupid%20not%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EIt's%20been%20much%20easier%20than%20I%20imagined%20it%20would%20be%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20remember%20when%20I%20met%20Brandt%2C%20he%20was%20telling%20me%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20bought%20this%20boat%20to%20live%20on%20it.%26quot%3B%20I%20was%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20can%20do%20that%3F%20That%20seems%20so%20challenging%20and%20crazy.%20I%20can't%20imagine%20all%20the%20adjustments%20you'd%20have%20to%20make%20to%20your%20lifestyle.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20surprising%20thing%20is%20actually%20how%20easy%20it's%20been%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0and%20we%20really%20haven't%20had%20to%20make%20many%20adjustments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20interior%20of%20the%20boat.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64ee530e26dda200194d4b3a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20interior%20of%20the%20boat.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Mikaella%20Taylor%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe're%20blessed%20with%20good%20weather%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20are%20always%20concerned%20about%20us%20when%20it's%20raining%20%E2%80%94%20but%20rain%20on%20the%20boat%20really%20isn't%20a%20challenge.%20It's%20a%20little%20uncomfortable%20because%20everything's%20wet%2C%20but%20aside%20from%20that%20we%20actually%20really%20like%20being%20inside%20the%20boat%20when%20it's%20raining.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20like%20being%20in%20your%20car%20when%20it%20rains.%20You%20hear%20that%20sound%20of%20the%20rain%20hitting%20the%20top%20of%20the%20boat.%20We%20just%20put%20on%20a%20good%20movie%20and%20make%20waffles%20and%20it's%20perfectly%20pleasant.%3