0said%20that%20we%20were%20always%20going%20to%20be%20in%20each%20other's%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20luckily%2C%20my%20fianc%C3%A9%20and%20I%20like%20each%20other%20so%20much.%20After%20a%20year%20we%20still%20very%20much%20like%20being%20around%20each%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EIt's%20brought%20us%20closer%20to%20nature%2C%20and%20made%20us%20more%20passionate%20about%20sustainability%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20always%20been%20really%20passionate%20about%20sustainability%2C%20which%20is%20also%20a%20reason%20that%20I%20really%20liked%20this%20lifestyle.%20It%20feels%20like%20a%20very%20sustainable%20way%20to%20live.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20feel%20so%20close%20to%20nature%20that%20it%20makes%20us%20more%20conscious%20of%20our%20impact%20on%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20lot%20of%20rain%2C%20there's%20usually%20so%20much%20trash%20floating%20in%20the%20water%20%E2%80%94%20it%20affects%20our%20home.%20Obviously%2C%20I%20think%20facing%20it%20makes%20me%20much%20more%20mindful%20of%20the%20waste%20that%20I%20am%20creating%20more%20than%2C%20I%20think%2C%20people%20who%20aren't%20near%20it%20and%20don't%20have%20to%20face%20it%20as%20often.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20also%20always%20been%20passionate%20about%20fashion.%20I%20was%20working%20on%20designing%20my%20own%20line%20of%20T-shirts%20and%20then%20started%20learning%20about%20the%20terrible%20impacts%20that%20some%20forms%20of%20fashion%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0like%20fast%20fashion%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffast-fashion-christmas-shopping-clothes-returns-shein-zara-waste-mountain-2022-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ehave%20on%20the%20environment%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222267%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22the%20couple%20in%20their%20boat%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64ee52be96b7920019c9eee8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221535%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ET