rturned%20its%20decision%20to%20block%20a%20spot%20Bitcoin%20exchange-traded%20fund%20proposed%20by%20Grayscale%20Investments.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGensler%20is%20undeterred%2C%20however%20%E2%80%93%20doubling%20down%20on%20his%20rhetoric%20as%20the%20SEC%20wades%20further%20into%20the%20cryptocurrency%20sphere.%20Here%2C%20Insider%20takes%20a%20look%20at%20his%20evolving%20stance%20on%20the%20industry.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EIn%20the%20beginning%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20Gensler's%20appointment%20to%20the%20SEC%20in%202021%2C%20and%20in%20the%20pre-Covid%20cryptocurrency%20boom%2C%20he%20was%20considerably%20more%20optimistic%20about%20the%20blockchain's%20prospects.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThough%20literally%20thousands%20of%20projects%20have%20yet%20to%20land%20on%20broadly%20adopted%20use%20cases%2C%20I%20remain%20intrigued%20by%20Satoshi's%20%5Bthe%20alleged%20creator%20of%20Bitcoin%5D%20innovation's%20potential%20to%20spur%20change%20%E2%80%93%20either%20directly%20or%20indirectly%20as%20a%20catalyst%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.coindesk.com%2Ftech%2F2019%2F12%2F15%2Feven-if-a-thousand-projects-dont-make-it-blockchain-is-still-a-change-catalyst%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ein%20an%20op-ed%20for%20CoinDesk%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20December%202019.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%26quot%3BThe%20potential%20to%20lower%20verification%20and%20networking%20costs%20is%20worth%20pursuing%2C%20particularly%20to%20lower%20economic%20rents%20and%20data%20privacy%20costs%2C%20and%20promote%20economic%20inclusion%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUpon%20his%20accession%20to%20the%20SEC%2C%20however%2C%20the%20former%20Goldman%20banker%20began%20using%20a%20'poker%20chips'%20analogy%20to%20describe%20the%20tokens.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20%24125%20billion%20of%20stablecoins%20we%20have%20right%20now%20are%20like%20poker%20chips%20at%20a%20casino%2C%26quot%3B%20Gensler%20told%20Congress%20in%20October%202021.%20%26quot%3BI%20do%20think%20that%20if%20this%20continues%20to%20grow%20%E2%80%93%20and%20it's%20grown%20about%20tenfold%20in%20the%20last%20year%20%E2%80%93%20it%20can%20present%20those%20systemic%20wide%20risks.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EGensler%20and%20the%20FTX%20fiasco%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20dramatic%20collapse%20of%20Sam%20Bankman-Fried's%20cryptocurrency%20exchange%20FTX%20in%20November%2C%20Gensler%20became%20considerably%20tougher%20on%20the%20industry%20after%20receiving%20blame%20for%20his%20role%20in%20the%20disaster.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%C2%A0This%20was%20down%20to%20lawmakers%20criticizing%20the%20SEC%20and%20Gensler%20himself%20for%20not%20being%20alert%20to%20FTX's%20wrongdoing%20sooner%20and%20failing%20to%20protect%20investors%20as%20the%20exchange%20collapsed%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.coindesk.com%2Fconsensus-magazine%2F2023%2F06%2F06%2Fgary-genslers-evolving-position-on-crypto-in-quotes%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20Coinbase%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20letter%20to%20the%20SEC%2C%20US%20representative%20Ritchie%20Torres%20labeled%20Gensler%20as%20%26quot%3Bsingularly%20responsible%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20FTX%20catastrophe%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffortune.com%2Fcrypto%2F2022%2F12%2F14%2Fgary-genslers-pr-stunts-cant-hide-how-he-botched-crypto-regulation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFortune%20Crypto%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%202023%20progresses%2C%20Gensler%20has%20become%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcurrencies%2Fcryptocurrency-rife-with-fraud-hucksters-warns-gary-gensler-sec-2023-7%5C%22%3Emore%20hardline%20on%20crypto%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20waging%20lawsuits%20not%20just%20against%20FTX%2C%20but%20also%20the%20Binance%20and%20Ripple%20platfor