ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Heath%20Streak%20passes%20away%3A%20Tributes%20pour%20in%20for%20Zimbabwe%20legend%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693734001000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-103325622%2Cimgsize-31516.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fnews%2Fheath-streak-passes-away-tributes-pour-in-for-zimbabwe-legend%2Farticleshow%2F103325637.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Cricketers%2C%20both%20past%20and%20present%2C%20paid%20rich%20tributes%20to%20former%20Zimbabwe%20captain%20Heath%20Streak%20who%20died%20on%20Sunday%20at%20the%20age%20of%2049.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20SPORTS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A11%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fnews%2Fheath-streak-passes-away-tributes-pour-in-for-zimbabwe-legend%2Farticleshow%2F103325637.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22INDIA%20Bloc%20%26quot%3BHates%20Hinduism%26quot%3B%3A%20Amit%20Shah%20On%20Row%20Over%20DMK%20Leader's%20Remark%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20remark%20on%20Sanatana%20Dharma%20by%20DMK%20chief%20MK%20Stalin's%20minister%20son%20shows%20that%20the%20Opposition%20bloc%20INDIA%20%26quot%3Bhates%20Hinduism%26quot%3B%20and%20is%20%26quot%3Ban%20attack%20on%20our%20heritage%26quot%3B%2C%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20said%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Shah%20was%20speaking%20at%20Dungarpur%20in%20poll-bound%20Rajasthan%20at%20the%20launch%20of%20BJP's%20Parivartan%20Yatra.%20The%20BJP%20is%20pushing%20hard%20to%20defeat%20the%20ruling%20Congress%20and%20return%20to%20power%20in%20the%20upcoming%20state%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Home%20Minister%20alleged%20that%20the%20remarks%20by%20Udhayanidhi%20Stalin%20are%20part%20of%20INDIA%20bloc's%20%26quot%3Bvote%20bank%20politics%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bappeasement%26quot%3B%20tactic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Home%20Minister's%20remarks%20come%20amid%20a%20huge%20row%20over%20remarks%20by%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Chief%20Minister%20MK%20Stalin's%20son%20Udhayanidhi.%C2%A0Addressing%20a%20writers'%20conference%20in%20Chennai%2C%20Udhayanidhi%20Stalin%20said%20the%20idea%20of%20%26quot%3BSanatana%20Dharma%20is%20against%20the%20idea%20of%20social%20justice%20and%20must%20be%20eradicated%26quot%3B.%20He%20also%20drew%20a%20parallel%20between%20Sanatana%20Dharma%20and%20diseases%20such%20as%20dengue%20and%20malaria.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20remarks%20went%20viral%2C%20BJP%20leaders%20termed%20them%20a%20call%20for%20genocide%20and%20slammed%20Udhayanidhi%20Stalin%20and%20questioned%20if%20all%20members%20of%20INDIA%20agree%20with%20the%20DMK%20leader's%20remarks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20the%20criticism%2C%20Mr%20Stalin%20has%20said%20Sanatana%20Dharma%20%26quot%3Bis%20a%20principle%20that%20divides%20people%20in%20the%20name%20of%20caste%20and%20religion%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20never%20called%20for%20the%20genocide%20of%20people%20who%20are%20following%20Sanatana%20Dharma.%20Uprooting%20Sanatana%20Dharma%20is%20upholding%20humanity%20and%20human%20equality.%20I%20stand%20firmly%20by%20every%20word%20I%20have%20spoken.%20I%20spoke%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20oppressed%20and%20marginalized%2C%20who%20suffer%20due%20to%20the%20Sanatana%20Dharma%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKarti%20Chidambaram%2C%20Congress%20leader%20and%20former%20Home%20Minister%20P%20Chidambaram's%20son%2C%20has%20backed%20the%20remarks%20by%20Udhayanidhi%20Stalin%2C%20saying%20that%20Sanatana%20Dharma%20%26quot%3Bis%20nothing%20but%20code%20for%20a%20Caste%20Hierarchical%20Society%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BAll%20those%20batting%20for%20it%20are%20hankering%20for%20the%20Good%20Ole%20Days!%20Caste%20is%20the%20curse%20of%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20has%20said.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESlamming%20DMK%20and%20the%20Congress%20over%20remarks%20by%20the%20two%20leaders%2C%20Mr%20Shah%20said%2C%C2%A0%26quot%3BOver%20the%20past%20two%20days%2C%20they%20(INDIA)%20are%20insulting%20this%20country's%20heritage%20and%20Sanatana%20Dharma.%20Sons%20of%20top%20leaders%20of%20Congress%20and%20DMK%20are%20talking%20about%20finishing%20Sanatana%20Dharma%20for%20the%20politics%20of%20vote%20bank%20and%20appeasement.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Home%20Minister%20also%20referred%20to%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%202010%20remark%2C%20in%20which%20he%20had%20said%20radical%20Hindu%20outfits%20are%20a%20bigger%20threat%20than%20terror%20organisation%20Lashkar-e-Taiba.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRahul%20Baba%20had%20said%20that%20Hindu%20organisations%20are%20more%20dangerous%20than%20Lashkar-e-Taiba.%20Rahul%20Baba%2C%20you%20compared%20Hindu%20organisations%20to%20Lashkar-e-Taiba%20and%20your%20Home%20Minister%20said%20there%20is%20'Hindu%20terror'%20in%20the%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Shah%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20referring%20to%20former%20Home%20Minister%20and%20Congress%20leader%20Sushil%20Kumar%20Shinde's%20remark%20on%20Hindu%20terror.%20Mr%20Shinde%20has%20said%20he%20had%20used%20the%20expression%20at%20a%20Jaipur%20party%20meeting%2C%20but%20withdrew%20it%20immediately.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20Rajasthan%20rally%2C%20Mr%20Shah%20said%20Sanatana%20Dharma%20is%20ruling%20the%20hearts%20of%20people.%20%26quot%3BThey%20say%20Sanatana%20rule%20will%20come%20if%20Modi%20wins.%20Sanatana%20is%20ruling%20people's%20heart%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20underlined%20that%20India%20will%20run%20as%20per%20the%20Constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccusing%20the%20Congress%20of%20blocking%20the%20construction%20of%20Ram%20Temple%20in%20Ayodhya%2C%20the%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Grand%20Ram%20temple%20will%20be%20ready%20in%20January%20at%20Lord%20Ram's%20birthplace.%20INDIA%20alliance%20cannot%20stop