training-for-marathon-4355314%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India%20Will%20Have%20No%20Place%20For%20Corruption%2C%20Casteism%2C%20Communalism%3A%20PM%20Modi%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndia%20will%20be%20a%20developed%20nation%20when%20it%20celebrates%20100%20years%20of%20Independence%2C%20and%20it%20will%20have%20no%20place%20for%20corruption%2C%20casteism%20and%20communalism%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20told%20news%20agency%20PTI%20in%20an%20interview%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndia%20will%20be%20a%20developed%20nation%20by%202047%3B%20corruption%2C%20casteism%20and%20communalism%20will%20have%20no%20place%20in%20our%20national%20life%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20the%20upcoming%20G20%20summit%20in%20New%20Delhi%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said%20the%20world%20now%20looks%20to%20India%20for%20guidance.%20%26quot%3BOur%20words%20and%20vision%20are%20seen%20by%20the%20world%20as%20a%20roadmap%20for%20the%20future%20and%20not%20merely%20ideas%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20The%20world's%20GDP-centric%20view%20is%20changing%20to%20a%20human-centric%20one%2C%20and%20India%20is%20playing%20the%20catalyst%20in%20this%20transformation%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStressing%20on%20how%20the%20world's%20perception%20of%20India%20is%20changing%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BFor%20long%2C%20India%20was%20seen%20as%20a%20country%20of%20one%20billion%20hungry%20stomachs.%20Now%20it%20is%20one%20billion%20aspirational%20minds%20and%20two%20billion%20skilled%20hands.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20said%20India's%20population%20can%20enable%20it%20to%20reap%20a%20massive%20demographic%20dividend%20over%20the%20next%20few%20decades.%20%26quot%3BIndians%20today%20have%20a%20great%20chance%20to%20lay%20the%20foundation%20for%20growth%20that%20will%20be%20remembered%20for%20the%20next%201%2C000%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%26quot%3BOnce%20seen%20simply%20as%20a%20large%20market%2C%20India%20now%20part%20of%20solutions%20to%20global%20challenges%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaking%20a%20swipe%20at%20Opposition%20parties%20and%20doubling%20down%20on%20his%20attack%20on%20what%20the%20BJP%20terms%20%26quot%3Bfreebie%20culture%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said%20%26quot%3Birresponsible%20financial%20policies%20and%20populism%20may%20give%20short-term%20political%20results%20but%20extract%20great%20social%2C%20economical%20price%20in%20the%20long%20term%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20another%20jab%20at%20the%20Opposition%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said%20previous%20governments%20%26quot%3Blacked%20confidence%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20people%20of%20other%20states%20to%20successfully%20execute%20high-profile%20global%20meets%20outside%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20G20%20Presidency%20has%20also%20sowed%20seeds%20of%20confidence%20in%20countries%20of%20the%20so-called%20Third%20World%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said.%C2%A0Amid%20the%20countdown%20for%20G20%2C%20the%20government%20has%20been%20underlining%20the%20role%20Third%20World%20countries%20--%20or%20Global%20South%20--%20will%20be%20playing%20in%20growth%20worldwide%20in%20the%20coming%20years.%20The%20Prime%20Minister%20has%20voiced%20the%20concerns%20and%20issues%20of%20Global%20South%20on%20several%20international%20fora.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20said%20India's%20domestic%20approach%20to%20address%20the%20most%20backward%20people%20also%20guides%20it%20at%20a%20global%20level%20as%20it%20voices%20the%20concerns%20of%20those%20neglected%20in%20the%20geopolitical%20landscape.%C2%A0%26quot%3BThe%20theme%20of%20India's%20G20%20Presidency%20'Vasudhaiva%20Kutumbakam'%20is%20not%20just%20a%20slogan%2C%20but%20a%20comprehensive%20philosophy%20derived%20from%20our%20cultural%20ethos%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20a%20question%20on%20the%20position%20India%20took%20on%20the%20Russia-Ukraine%20war%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20reiterated%20that%20dialogue%20and%20diplomacy%20are%20the%20only%20way%20to%20resolve%20conflicts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20refusal%20to%20side%20with%20any%20camp%20and%20consistently%20advocate%20dialogue%20during%20the%20Ukraine%20conflict%20had%20sparked%20criticism%20from%20some%20quarters.%20Some%20voices%20in%20the%20West%20had%20also%20slammed%20India's%20decision%20to%20buy%20fuel%20from%20Russia%20even%20after%20the%20Vladimir%20Putin%20dispensation%20faced%20sanctions%20from%20Europe%20and%20the%20US.%C2%A0India%20has%20firmly%20defended%20its%20decision%2C%20with%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20Dr%20S%20Jaishankar%20saying%20that%20every%20country%20was%20trying%20to%20get%20the%20best%20possible%20deal%20for%20its%20citizens%20and%20India%20was%20no%20different.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhether%20as%20G20%20President%20or%20not%2C%20we%20will%20support%20every%20effort%20to%20ensure%20peace%20across%20the%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20climate%20change%2C%20an%20issue%20on%20which%20India%20has%20called%20upon%20developed%20countries%20to%20do%20more%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said%20%26quot%3Bthere%20are%20no%20one-size-fits-all%20solutions%20in%20fighting%20climate%20change%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693728240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2F0bdqqnno_pm-modi-pti-650_650x400_10_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcorruption-casteism-and-communalism-will-have-no-place-in-our-national-life-pm-narendra-modi-to-news-agency-pti-4355051%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%20will%20be%20a%20developed%20nation%20when%20it%20celebrates%20100%20years%20of%20Independence%2C%20and%20it%20will%20have%20no%20place%20for%20corruption%2C%20casteism%20and%20communalism%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20told%20news%20agency%20PTI%20in%20an%20interview%20today.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcorruption-casteism-and-communalism-will-have-no-place-in-our-national-life-pm-narendra-modi-to-news-agency-pti-4355051%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcorruption-casteism-and-communalism-will-have-no-place-in-our-national-life-pm-narendra-modi-to-news-agency-pti-4355051%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcorruption-casteism-and-communalism-will-have-no-place-in-our-national-life-pm-narendra-modi-to-news-agency-pti-4355051%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Talk%20of%20%E2%80%98Sub-Categorisation%E2%80%99%20of%20OBC%20Benefits%20Meaningless%20Without%20Caste%20Census%3A%20National%20Backward%20Commission%20Ex-Chief%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F11%2F22141813%2Fnalsar-final.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20After%2016%20extensions%2C%20the%20long-awaited%20Rohini%20Commission%20set%20up%20in%202017%2C%20has%20finally%20submitted%20its%20report%20last%20month.%20It%20is%20expected%20to%20have%20proposed%20the%20sub-categorisation%20of%20the%20Central%20List%20of%20OBCs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20former%20chairperson%20of%20the%20National%20Commission%20for%20Backward%20Classes%20(NCBC)%2C%20Justice%20Vangala%20Eswaraiah%2C%20has%20hit%20out%20at%20the%20drive%20to%20look%20at%20%E2%80%98sub-categorisation%E2%80%99%20without%20a%20caste%20census%2C%20calling%20it%20a%20mistake.%20He%20has%20called%20for%20the%20findings%20to%20be%20%E2%80%9Cdumped.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fepaper.newindianexpress.com%2Ft%2F3353%5C%22%3EHe%20told%20the%3Cem%3E%20New%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20government%20will%20implement%20the%20report%20as%20it%20wants%20to%20appease%20the%20OBCs%20as%20a%20poll%20strategy.%20The%20Rohini%20Commission%20should%20be%20dumped%20as%20it%20is.%20How%20can%20it%20reflect%20the%20caste%20reality%20without%20undertaking%20any%20survey%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20caste%20census%20for%20India%20was%20done%20in%201931%2C%20before%20independence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fformer-ncbc-chief-without-caste-census-obc-sub-categorisation-not-scientific-7203445%2F%5C%22%3EIn%202021%2C%20Justice%20Easwaraiah%20had%20told%20the%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20without%20a%20caste%20census%2C%20this%20%5Bof%20sub-categorisation%20of%20OBC%20castes%5D%20exercise%20%E2%80%9Ccould%20perpetuate%20injustice.%E2%80%9D%20He%20had%20then%20termed%20the%20sub-categorisation%2C%20which%20was%20likely%20to%20be%20proposed%20by%20the%20Commission%20headed%20by%20Justice%20G%20Rohini%2C%20as%20%E2%80%9Cun-scientific%2C%20atrocious%20and%20illegal%E2%80%9D.%20Justice%20Eswaraiah%20had%20also%20said%20if%20the%20government%20wants%20to%20sub-categorise%20the%20OBCs%20in%20order%20to%20give%20them%20justice%2C%20it%20should%20either%20publicise%20the%20data%20of%20Socio%20Economic%20and%20Caste%20Census%20(SECC)-2011%20or%20it%20should%20conduct%20a%20caste%20census.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fmajor-departure-justice-g-rohini-commission-recommends-overhaul-of-obc-quota-allocation-in-voluminous-report-101693596065371.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20on%20Saturday%2C%20September%202%2C%202023%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%20on%20the%20Rohini%20Commission%20citing%20sources%20as%20saying%20that%20%E2%80%9Cit%20%5Bsub-categorisation%5D%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20three%20or%20four%20where%20the%20castes%20with%20similar%20access%20to%20benefits%20compete%20with%20each%20other.%20It%20could%20be%20three%20bands%20%E2%80%94%20those%20that%20have%20got%20no%20benefits%20could%20get%2010%25%2C%20those%20with%20some%20benefits%2010%25%2C%20and%20those%20with%20maximum%20benefits%207%25%20%E2%80%93%20or%20there%20could%20also%20be%20four%20bands.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20mandate%20of%20the%20Rohini%20Commission%20was%20to%20study%20how%20benefits%20within%20the%20OBCs%20should%20be%20divided%20and%20also%20update%20the%20list%20of%202633%20OBC%20groups.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newindianexpress.com%2Fnation%2F2023%2Faug%2F02%2Fcentremay-tread-cautiously-over-rohini-commission-report-on-sub-categorisation-of-obcs-2601078.html%5C%22%3EIn%202018%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20sharing%20its%20findings%20publicly%2C%20the%20Rohini%20Commission%20said%20that%20less%20than%201%25%20of%20backward%20castes%20have%20cornered%2050%25%20of%20the%20reservation%20benefits%20in%20admissions%20to%20Central%20educational%20institutions%20and%20jobs%20in%20Central%20services%20between%202014%20and%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20government%20is%20in%20a%20corner%20over%20Justice%20G.%20Rohini%E2%80%99s%20recommendations%2C%20in%20case%20the%20report%20actually%20suggests%20tiers%20within%20OBC%20reservations%2C%20as%20in%20an%20election%20year%2C%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20report%20is%20bound%20to%20open%20a%20Pandora%E2%80%99s%20box.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Modi%20government%20has%20been%20on%20the%20defensive%20and%20uneasy%20over%20demands%20for%20a%20caste%20census%20rapidly%20gaining%20ground.%20Opposition%20parties%20support%20the%20move%2C%20Bihar%20has%20completed%20its%20census%20and%20work%20is%20underway%20in%20Odisha%20and%20Jharkhand.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693727875000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F11%2F22141813%2Fnalsar-final.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Ftalk-of-sub-categorisation-of-obc-benefits-meaningless-without-caste-census-national-backward-c