t%20their%20influx%20would%20not%20turn%20the%20country%20into%20%26quot%3Bthe%20filth%20that%20is%20India%26quot%3B%2C%20according%20to%20a%20media%20report.%20Pollitt%20later%20apologised%20to%20Kumar%2C%20in%20an%20email%20saying%20she%20did%20not%20intend%20to%20be%20racist.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Faustralian-real-estate-agent-suspended-after-sending-racist-email-to-indian-tenant%2Farticleshow%2F103324036.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Faustralian-real-estate-agent-suspended-after-sending-racist-email-to-indian-tenant%2Famp_articleshow%2F103324036.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Faustralian-real-estate-agent-suspended-after-sending-racist-email-to-indian-tenant%2Famp_articleshow%2F103324036.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22When%20Miley%20Cyrus%20spoke%20about%20Tachyeardia%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693727055000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-103323985%2Cimgsize-35500.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fenglish%2Fhollywood%2Fnews%2Fdid-you-know-miley-cyrus-has-heart-condition-called-tachyeardia%2Farticleshow%2F103323892.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F103323892.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EA%20few%20years%20ago%2C%20the%20Wrecking%20Ball%20singer%20had%20revealed%20that%20she%20suffers%20from%20Tachycardia%20-%20a%20faster%20than%20normal%20heartbeat%20condition.%20Read%20on%20to%20know%20all%20that%20Miley%20Cyrus%20shared%20about%20her%20health%20condition.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Opinion%3A%20Diversity%20In%20Unity%20-%20After%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%2C%20Nitish%20Kumar%2C%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20Skip%20Joint%20INDIA%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20triple%20jump%2C%20sometimes%20referred%20to%20as%20hop%2C%20skip%20and%20jump%2C%20is%20a%20track%20and%20field%20event%2C%20similar%20to%20long%20jump%20in%20sport.%20The%20conglomerate%20of%2028%20parties%20with%20a%20pretentious%20and%20confusing%20name%2C%20I.N.D.I.A%20(Indian%20National%20Developmental%20Inclusive%20Alliance)%20seems%20to%20be%20afflicted%20by%20hops%20and%20skips%20of%20key%20participants%2C%20all%20Chief%20Ministers%20and%20leaders%20of%20prominent%20state%20parties%2C%20prior%20to%20the%20alliance%20jumping%20to%20emerge%20as%20a%20viable%20alternative%20to%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20his%20NDA%20(National%20Democratic%20Alliance).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEach%20of%20its%20three%20conclaves%20has%20been%20marked%20by%20a%20prominent%20party%20chief%20who%20is%20also%20a%20Chief%20Minister%20throw%20tantrums%20and%20hop%20out%20at%20the%20end%2C%20skipping%20the%20grand%20finale.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Patna%2C%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20left%20prior%20to%20the%20joint%20media%20briefing%20as%20he%20had%20a%20%26quot%3Bflight%20to%20catch%26quot%3B.%20Nitish%20Kumar%2C%20accompanied%20by%20Lalu%20Yadav%20and%20his%20son%20Tejashwi%2C%20similarly%20rushed%20back%20to%20Patna.%20In%20Mumbai%2C%20Mamata%20Banerjee%2C%20accompanied%20by%20nephew%20Abhishek%20Banerjee%20and%20party%20leader%20Derek%20O'Brien%20dashed%20to%20Kolkata%2C%20skipping%20the%20media%20interaction%20by%20other%20leaders%20of%20I.N.D.I.A.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMamata%20Banerjee%20usually%20does%20not%20use%20commercial%20flights%3B%20West%20Bengal%20hires%20aircraft%20for%20her.%20Nitish%20Kumar%20and%20Lalu%20Yadav%20too%20had%20a%20special%20aircraft.%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%2C%20accompanied%20by%20Punjab%20Chief%20Minister%20Bhagwant%20Mann%2C%20travels%20by%20the%20Punjab%20state%20plane.%20The%20departure%20time%20of%20all%20three%20flights%20could%20have%20been%20flexible%20to%20suit%20the%20programme%20of%20the%20conclaves.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%224iq4e9v8%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2F4iq4e9v8_india-bloc_625x300_01_September_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two-day%20Mumbai%20conclave%20did%20not%20throw%20up%20a%20convener.%20Or%20a%20common%20logo%2C%20as%20hyped%20in%20the%20media%20before%20the%20meeting.%20Initially%2C%20the%20plan%20was%20for%20the%20conclave%20to%20culminate%20in%20a%20public%20meeting%20at%20the%20Shivaji%20Park%20in%20Dadar.%20There%20was%20no%20mention%20of%20this%20plan%20during%20the%20two-day%20meet.%20The%20ability%20of%20factions%20of%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20and%20NCP%20that%20are%20part%20of%20the%20alliance%2C%20along%20with%20the%20Maharashtra%20Pradesh%20Congress%2C%20to%20mobilise%20an%20impressive%20gathering%20in%20Mumbai%20was%20an%20option%20which%20went%20off%20the%20radar%20somewhere%20midway.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two-day%20deliberation%20was%20reflected%20in%20a%20one-page%20resolution%20in%20which%20the%20intent%20to%20contest%20the%202024%20general%20elections%20together%20%26quot%3Bas%20far%20as%20possible%26quot%3B%20was%20chronicled.%20The%20distance%20to%20be%20traversed%20was%20left%20ambiguous.%20Intra-state%20differences%20of%20the%2028%20%26quot%3Bpartners%26quot%3B%20apparently%20had%20not%20been%20papered%20over.%20No%20political%20resolution%20was%20adopted%2C%20thus%20betraying%20the%20possibility%20of%20lack%20of%20unanimity%20on%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20one-page%20resolution%2C%20which%20is%20unprecedented%20in%20India's%20political%20history%20due%20to%20its%20brevity%2C%20said%20that%20seat%20sharing%20arrangements%20%26quot%3Bwill%20be%20initiated%20immediately%20and%20concluded%20at%20the%20earliest%20in%20the%20collaborative%20spirit%20of%20give%20and%20take%26quot%3B.%20The%20inability%20to%20set%20a%20timeline%20on%20seat-sharing%20miffed%20Mamata%20Banerjee%2C%20necessitating%20her%20hurry%20to%20catch%20a%20flight%20back%20to%20Kolkata.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMamata%20wanted%20seat%20sharing%20to%20be%20decided%20by%20the%20third%20week%20of%20September.%20Sitaram%20Yechury%20of%20CPI(M)%20suggested%20that%20the%20timeline%20be%20flexible%2C%20and%20that%20seat%20sharing%20be%20discussed%20not%20on%20the%20national%2C%20but%20at%20the%20state-to-state%20level.(Will%20Mamata's%20and%20Yechury's%20parties%20share%20seats%20in%20West%20Bengal%3F)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20alliance%20plans%20one-on-one%20contests%20against%20the%20NDA%20in%20400%20to%20440%20of%20the%20545%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats.%20A%2014-member%20apex%20committee%20was%20set%20up%2C%20which%20includes%20heavyweight%20Sharad%20Pawar%20of%20NCP%20(Sharad)%20alongside%20Abhishek%20Banerjee%20(Trinamool)%2C%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%20(RJD)%2C%20Omar%20Abdullah%20(Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20National%20Conference)%2C%20and%20Mehbooba%20Mufti%20(PDP).%20This%20and%20the%20other%20four%20panels%20announced%20in%20Mumbai%20lacked%20gravitas%3B%20mostly%20second%20and%20third%20rung%20leaders%20were%20chosen%20by%20parties%20as%20nominees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22tg2n9v3g%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Ftg2n9v3g_india-alliance-mumbai-meeting-650_625x300_01_September_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaghav%20Chadha%20emerged%20as%20the%20prominent%20face%20of%20AAP%20by%20being%20included.%20The%20CPI(M)%20did%20not%20finalise%20its%20nominee%20for%20the%20apex%20panel%20though%20it%20named%20members%20to%20the%20other%20sub-panels%20which%20were%20set%20up.%20The%20CPI%20put%20up%20its%20top%20man%20D%20Raja.%20The%20Congress%20is%20represented%20by%20its%20organisation%20secretary%2C%20KC%20Venugopal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20emerging%20face%20at%20Mumbai%20was%20that%20of%20Abhishek%20Banerjee.%20His%20air%20dash%20to%20Delhi%20to%20have%20a%20powwow%20with%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20on%20the%20eve%20of%20the%20Mumbai%20meet%20showed%20that%20Congress-Trinamool%20ties%20are%20no%20longer%20Sonia%20Gandhi-Mamata%20centric.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Trinamool%20Congress%20did%20not%20finalise%20its%20name%20for%20any%20of%20the%20other%20four%20panels%3A%20the%20campaign%20committee%2C%20social%20media%20committee%2C%20media%20committee%20and%20a%20research%20committee.%20The%20Congress%20nominated%20its%20social%20media%20head%2C%20Supriya%20Shrinate%2C%20in%20the%20panel%20of%20her%20subject%2C%20but%20her%20counterpart%2C%20media%20department%20head%20Pawan%20Khera%2C%20did%20not%20find%20a%20place%20in%20the%20media%20committee%2C%20where%20party%20general%20secretary%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20did.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sudden%20entry%20of%20eminent%20lawyer%20Kapil%20Sibal%2C%20a%20prominent%20face%20in%20the%20Opposition%20ranks%20who%20is%20active%20both%20in%20parliament%20and%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20upset%20the%20Congress.%20Sibal%2C%20part%20of%20the%20%26quot%3BG23%26quot%3B%20reform%20brigade%2C%20left%20the%20Grand%20Old%20Party%20(which%20he%20had%20joined%20at%20the%20instance%20of%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20in%201991)%20in%202022%20and%20was%20elected%20to%20Rajya%20Sabha%20from%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20supported%20by%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party.%20No%20one%20seemed%20to%20know%20who%20had%20invited%20Sibal%20to%20this%20joint%20meeting%20of%20national%20and%20state%20parties.%20Speculation%20ranged%20from%20joint%20hosts%20Sharad%20Pawar%20and%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20to%20Farooq%20Abdullah%20and%20Sibal's%20latest%20benefactor%2C%20Akhilesh%20Yadav.%20Sibal%20is%20representing%20cases%20of%20many%20opposition%20parties%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20and%20is%20a%20confidant%20of%20a%20mosaic%20of%20party%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22p7000kq%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fp7000kq_kapil-sibal-at-india-meet-ani-650_650x400_01_September_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20glitches%20apart%2C%20the%20intent%20and%20determination%20evidenced%20in%20Patna%20and%20Bengaluru%20were%20somewhat%20absent%20in%20Mumbai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20venue%20of%20the%20next%20meeting%20has%20not%20been%20declared.%20Speculation%20is%20that%20it%20may%20be%20Bhopal.%20With%20Kamal%20Nath%20at%20the%20helm%20of%20the%20Congress%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20a%20conclave%20in%20the%20state%20capital%20will%20certainly%20aid%20the%20party's%20campaign%20in%20this%20poll-bound%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20announcement%20of%20the%20next%20venue%20was%20kept%20in%20abeyance%20apparently%20as%20CPI%20(M)%20secretary%20Sitaram%20Yechury%20advised%20against%20holding%20a%20meeting%20in%20any%20state%20where%20assembly%20elections%20are%20due%20later%20this%20year.%20The%20communist%20leader%2C%20an%20expert%20on%20dialectics%2C%20cautioned%20that%20alliance%20partners%20may%20contest%20against%20each%20other%20in%20state%20polls%20and%20this%20may%20distract%20from%20the%20focus%20on%20uniting%20against%20the%20NDA%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYechury%20perhaps%20factored%20in%20the%20recent%20forays%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%2C%20accompanied%20by%20Bhagwant%20Mann%2C%20has%20been%20making%20in%20Congress-ruled%20Chhattisgarh%20and%20Rajasthan%20(where%20he%20offered%20voters%20agendas%20different%20from%20those%20of%20Chief%20Ministers%20Bhupesh%20Baghel%20and%20Ashok%20Gehlot)%20and%20into%20the%20Congress-dominated%20opposition%20turf%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20scenario%20emerging%20for%20the%20next%20general%20election%20is%20similar%20to%20that%20of%201971%2C%20when%20a%20combined%20opposition%20tried%20to%20oust%20a%20strong%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20Indira%20Gandhi.%20Their%20war%20cry%20%26quot%3BIndira%20%3Cem%3Ehatao%3C%2Fem%3E%26quot%3B%20was%20effectively%20countered%20by%20Indira%20Gandhi's%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3Egaribi%20hatao%3C%2Fem%3E%26quot%3B.%20Will%20Narendra%20Modi's%20aspirational%20%C2%A0%26quot%3BAmritkaal%26quot%3B%20stymie%20a%20similar%20Charge%20of%20the%20Light%20Brigade%20now%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20opposition%20has%20questioned%20the%20timing%20of%20the%20special%20session%20of%20parliament%20convened%20in%20September.%20The%20prerogative%20of%20summoning%20parliament%20and%20setting%20an%20agenda%20lies%20with%20the%20ruling%20party%20of%20the%20day.%20The%20one-page%20resolution%20of%20Mumbai%20does%20not%20elaborate%20how%20the%20alliance%20plans%20to%20offset%20Narendra%20Modi's%20agenda-setting%20juggernaut.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Shubhabrata%20Bhattacharya%20is%20a%20retired%20Editor%20and%20a%20public%20affairs%20commentator)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693727040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2F4dm2m8do_india-bloc_625x300_01_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fdiversity-in-unity-after-arvind-kejriwal-nitish-kumar-mamata-banerjee-skip-joint-india-briefing-4355254%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20scenario%20emerging%20for%20the%20next%20general%20election%20is%20similar%20to%20that%20of%201971%2C%20when%20a%20combined%20opposition%20tried%20to%20oust%20a%20strong%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20Indira%20Gandhi.%20Their%20war%20cry%20%26quot%3BIndira%20hatao%26quot%3B%20was%20effectively%20countered%20by%20Indira%20Gandhi's%20%26quot%3Bgaribi%20hatao%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fdiversity-in-unity-after-arvind-kejriwal-nitish-kumar-mamata-banerjee-skip-joint-india-briefing-4355254%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fdiversity