%20the%20platform%20formerly%20known%20as%20Twitter%20(now%20X)%2C%20Mr%20Mahindra%C2%A0%20spoke%20about%20his%20first%20encounter%20with%20Mr%20Kotak.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EHe%20recalled%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20remember%20the%20first%20time%20I%20met%20Uday%20when%20he%20walked%20into%20my%20Office%20at%20Mahindra%20Ugine%20Steel%20almost%204%20decades%20ago%20and%20offered%20me%20a%20bill-discounting%20faculty.%20The%20alloy%20steel%20industry%20was%20in%20a%20trough%20at%20that%20time%20and%20I%20asked%20him%20why%20he%20was%20taking%20the%20risk.%20He%20replied%3A%20%E2%80%98I've%20studied%20both%20the%20company%20and%20the%20management%20%26amp%3B%20concluded%20my%20money%20will%20be%20safe.'%20He%20was%20only%20in%20his%20early%20twenties%20but%20I%20clearly%20saw%20the%20signs%20of%20a%20very%20special%20mind.%20I%20vividly%20recall%20telling%20him%20that%20if%20he%20ever%20needed%20outside%20capital%20to%20come%20back%20to%20me%2C%20%26amp%3B%20to%20my%20great%20good%20fortune%2C%20he%20did!%20The%20rest%2C%20as%20they%20say%2C%20is%20history.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EExtending%20his%20best%20wishes%20to%20Mr%20Kotak%2C%20Mr%20Mahindra%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CBut%20there%20is%20no%20finish%20line%20to%20%E2%80%98His-story.'%20Uday's%20simply%20starting%20a%20new%20chapter%20of%20impact%20on%20the%20Indian%20Financial%20services%20Industry.%20Here's%20to%20more%20adventures%2C%20my%20friend!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EI%20remember%20the%20first%20time%20I%20met%20Uday%20when%20he%20walked%20into%20my%20Office%20at%20Mahindra%20Ugine%20Steel%20almost%204%20decades%20ago%20%26amp%3B%20offered%20me%20a%20bill-discounting%20faculty.%20The%20alloy%20steel%20industry%20was%20in%20a%20trough%20at%20that%20time%20and%20I%20asked%20him%20why%20he%20was%20taking%20the%20risk.%20He%20replied%3A%20%E2%80%9CI've%20studied%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FGcUq272Ku0%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FGcUq272Ku0%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20anand%20mahindra%20(%40anandmahindra)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fanandmahindra%2Fstatus%2F1697981084422885882%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ESeptember%202%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EOn%20Saturday%2C%20at%20the%20time%20of%20announcing%20his%20resignation%2C%20Mr%20Kotak%20tweeted%2C%20%E2%80%9CSuccession%20at%20Kotak%20Mahindra%20Bank%20has%20been%20foremost%20on%20my%20mind%2C%20since%20our%20Chairman%2C%20myself%20and%20Joint%20MD%20are%20all%20required%20to%20step%20down%20by%20year%20end.%20I%20am%20keen%20to%20ensure%20a%20smooth%20transition%20by%20sequencing%20these%20departures.%20I%20initiate%20this%20process%20now%20and%20step%20down%20voluntarily%20as%20CEO.%20The%20bank%20awaits%20RBI%20approval%20of%20the%20proposed%20successor.%20In%20the%20interim%20my%20dear%20colleague%20Dipak%20Gupta%20-%20currently%20Joint%20MD%2C%20will%20function%20as%20MD%20%26amp%3B%20CEO%2C%20subject%20to%20approvals.%20As%20Founder%2C%20I%20am%20deeply%20attached%20to%20the%20brand%20Kotak%20and%20will%20continue%20to%20serve%20the%20institution%20as%20Non-Executive%20Director%20and%20significant%20shareholder.%20We%20have%20an%20outstanding%20management%20team%20to%20carry%20the%20legacy%20forward.%20Founders%20go%20away%2C%20but%20the%20institution%20flourishes%20into%20perpetuity.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EReflecting%20on%20his%20remarkable%2038-year%20journey%2C%20Mr%20Kotak%20shared%2C%20%E2%80%9CA%20long%20time%20ago%2C%20I%20saw%20names%20like%20JP%20Morgan%20and%20Goldman%20Sachs%20dominate%20the%20financial%20world%20and%20dreamed%20of%20creating%20such%20an%20institution%20in%20India.%20It%20is%20with%20this%20dream%20that%20I%20started%20Kotak%20Mahindra%2038%20years%20ago%2C%20with