98Antara%E2%80%99%20at%20Neom%E2%80%99s%20Bajdah%20Studios%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693724610000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FNeom.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1235711965%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22British%20Hollywood%20director%20Simon%20West%20(%E2%80%9CCon%20Air%2C%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%9CLara%20Croft%3ATomb%20Raider%E2%80%9D)%20is%20set%20to%20direct%20Saudi%20Arabia-set%20epic%20%E2%80%9CAntara%E2%80%9D%20that%20will%20be%20shot%20in%20Neom%2C%20the%20sprawling%20production%20hub%20in%20Saudi%20Arabia%E2%80%99s%20northwestern%20corner.%20The%20English-language%20blockbuster%20based%20on%20Arab%20history%20is%20the%20tale%20of%C2%A0Antara%20ibn%20Shaddad%2C%20a%20slave%20warrior%20who%20was%20propelled%20to%20mythical%20status%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Nvivarelli%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Ffilm%2Fglobal%2Ftomb-raider-simon-west-saudi-arabia-set-epic-antara-at-neom-1235711965%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Ffilm%2Fglobal%2Ftomb-raider-simon-west-saudi-arabia-set-epic-antara-at-neom-1235711965%2Famp%2F%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Ffilm%2Fglobal%2Ftomb-raider-simon-west-saudi-arabia-set-epic-antara-at-neom-1235711965%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BRakesh%20Ji...%26quot%3B%3A%20Ameesha%20On%20Kareena's%20Exit%20From%20Kaho%20Naa...%20Pyaar%20Hai%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAmeesha%20Patel%2C%20who%20is%20basking%20in%20the%20success%20of%3Ci%3E%20Gadar%202%3C%2Fi%3E%2C%20has%20revealed%20Kareena%20Kapoor%20was%20asked%20to%20leave%20%3Ci%3EKaho%20Naa...%20Pyaar%20Hai%3C%2Fi%3E.%20In%20case%20you%20don't%20know%2C%20Kareena%2C%20who%20marked%20her%20Bollywood%20debut%20with%20Abhishek%20Bachchan's%20%3Ci%3ERefugee%20%3C%2Fi%3Ein%202000%2C%20was%20initially%20set%20to%20debut%20alongside%20Hrithik%20Roshan%20in%20%3Ci%3EKaho%20Naa%E2%80%A6%20Pyaar%20Hai%3C%2Fi%3E.%20But%20after%20shooting%20for%20a%20few%20days%2C%20Kareena%20was%20replaced%20by%20Ameesha.%20While%20earlier%20reports%20suggested%20that%20Kareena's%20mother%2C%20Babita%20Kapoor%2C%20pulled%20her%20out%20of%20the%20project%20as%20she%20wasn't%20satisfied%20with%20how%20the%20story%20was%20coming%20out%2C%20Ameesha%20claimed%20that%20%E2%80%9Che%20%5BRakesh%20Roshan%5D%20had%20asked%20her%20%5BKareena%5D%20to%20leave%20the%20film.%E2%80%9D%20In%20a%20conversation%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DkEa17kAvsSo%5C%22%3EBollywood%20Bubble%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Ameesha%20revealed%20that%20Rakesh%20Roshan%20and%20Kareena%20had%20differences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmeesha%20Patel%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CActually%2C%20she%20didn't%20back%20out.%20From%20what%20Rakesh%20ji%20told%20me%2C%20he%20asked%20her%20to%20leave%20the%20film%20because%20they%20were%20having%20differences.%E2%80%9D%20The%20%3Ci%3EGadar%202%3C%2Fi%3E%20actress%20revealed%20that%20the%20makers%20had%20to%20find%20%3Ci%3ESonia's%20%3C%2Fi%3E%5Bthe%20character%20played%20by%20Ameesha%5D%20replacement%20in%20three%20days%2C%20as%20the%20set%20was%20ready.%20She%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CAnd%20Pinkie%20%5BRoshan%5D%20aunty%2C%20his%20wife%20and%20Hrithik's%20mom%2C%20said%20that%20they%20were%20shocked%20because%20the%20set%20was%20ready%2C%20and%20a%20replacement%20%3Ci%3ESonia%20%3C%2Fi%3Ehad%20to%20be%20found%20in%20three%20days%2C%20and%20crores%20of%20rupees%20(had%20been%20spent)%20on%20that%20set%2C%20and%20it%20was%20Hrithik's%20debut%20and%20everyone%20was%20stressed.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmeesha%20Patel%20added%20that%20Rakesh%20Roshan%20saw%20her%20at%20a%20wedding%20and%20decided%20to%20cast%20her.%20The%20actress%20also%20said%20that%20when%20she%20was%20offered%20%3Ci%3EKaho%20Naa%E2%80%A6%20Pyaar%20Hai%3C%2Fi%3E%2C%20she%20had%20no%20i