0history%2C%20during%20the%20officially%20declared%20%E2%80%98Swarn%20Yug%E2%80%99%2C%20or%20the%20Golden%20Period%2C%20or%20Amritkaals%2C%20most%20prefer%20succumbing%20to%20the%20vision%20of%20progress%20that%20leads%20nations%20to%20a%20radiant%20future%20a%20few%20years%20down%20the%20line.%20However%2C%20such%20literary%20craft%20often%20slyly%20undermines%20such%20stentorian%20high%20seriousness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGreat%20writers%20have%20often%20recorded%20tales%20about%20a%20very%20different%20face%20of%20totalitarianism%2C%20one%20that%20a%20benign%20child%2C%20hugging%20and%20backslapping%2C%20reveals%20in%20private.%20It%20is%20dark%2C%20menacing%2C%20undemocratic%20and%20morbid.%20From%20the%20humble%20Dalit%20poet%20Kumbhandas%2C%20sniggering%20at%20those%20queuing%20up%20to%20visit%20the%20capital%20Sikri%20to%20meet%20the%20Patsah%2C%20to%20a%20forest%20dwelling%20Sufi%20Jayasi%20with%20matted%20hair%20and%20torn%20clothes%20who%20asked%20the%20Sultan%2C%20%E2%80%98do%20you%20ridicule%20me%20or%20my%20maker%3F%E2%80%99%2C%20there%20is%20a%20long%20list%20of%20saint%20poets%20who%20watched%20parades%20of%20ephemeral%20power%20ironically.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUniversally%2C%20writers%2C%20through%20their%20personal%20and%20collective%20experiences%2C%20often%20refrain%20from%20waving%20flags%2C%20worshipping%20at%20the%20grand%20statues%20of%20history%20and%20eulogizing%20the%20benevolence%20and%20divine%20stature%20of%20mortal%20regimes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20does%20a%20saint%20need%20from%20Sikri%3F%20Your%20sandals%20wear%20down%20during%20the%20long%20journey%20and%20you%20forget%20your%20Lord%E2%80%99s%20name%2C%E2%80%9Dthe%20poet%20Kumbhandas%20had%20said%2C%20some%20five%20centuries%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20meets%20Kumbhandas%E2%80%99s%20spiritual%20brother%20in%20the%20great%20Czech%20writer%20from%20Prague%2C%20Jaroslav%20Hasek%2C%20a%20drunk%20and%20an%20eccentric%20man%20in%20his%20personal%20life%2C%20but%20the%20writer%20of%20a%20great%20comic%20novel%20about%20the%20serious%20business%20of%20World%20War%20and%20its%20heroes.%20In%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Good%20Soldier%20Schweik%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20bedraggled%20protagonist%20reduces%20war%20and%20the%20awesome%20tyrant%20wearing%20all%20his%20medals%20to%20a%20joke%20with%20his%20exaggerated%20acts%20of%20subservience%20and%20by%20raising%20patriotic%20slogans%20suddenly%20after%20he%20has%20delivered%20a%20stirring%20speech%20and%20all%20routine%20clapping%20has%20died%20down.%20The%20very%20verbosity%20of%20his%20repeated%20shows%20of%20patriotism%20and%20devotion%20for%20the%20nation%20and%20the%20leader%20drive%20home%20the%20point%20far%20more%20effectively%20than%20any%20dark%20philosophical%20treatise%20on%20tyranny%20and%20destructive%20forces%20of%20a%20world%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20same%20literary%20cauldron%20in%20Prague%20also%20produced%20another%20great%20writer%2C%20Kafka.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKafka%2C%20who%20came%20from%20a%20middle-class%20background%2C%20was%20brought%20up%20as%20a%20Jew%20in%20the%20liberal%20city%20of%20Prague.%20He%20was%20both%20enamoured%20and%20horrified%20by%20the%20anti-Semitism%20experienced%20by%20his%20people%20from%20the%20eastern%20ghettoes.%20His%20writing%20takes%20us%20from%20the%20concrete%20to%20the%20metaphorical%20to%20the%20allegorical%20descriptions%20of%20the%20surrealistic%20mindset%20unleashed%20in%20Europe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20writings%20resonate%20with%20the%20sheer%20absurdity%20of%20human%20civilisation%2C%20suddenly%20pitted%20against%20a%20vast%20labyrinthine%20bureaucratic%20machine.%20Wandering%20in%20these%20lanes%20we%20see%20alienation%20from%20oneself%2C%20a%20long%20convoluted%20history%20of%20migrant%20forefathers%2C%20losing%20an%20identity%20enjoyed%20since%20birth%20without%20gaining%20another.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20does%20a%20writer%20face%20it%3F%20In%20one%20of%20his%20best%20known%20stories%2C%20Kafka%E2%80%99s%20Gregor%20Samsa%20wakes%20up%20one%20morning%20to%20find%20himself%20turned%20into%20a%20gigantic%20cockroach%2C%20lying%20on%20his%20back%2C%20frantically%20trying%20to%20stand%20on%20his%20feet%20with%20his%20hind%20legs%2C%20still%20stuck%20in%20sticky%20ancestral%20secretions!%20Today%20this%20poignant%20helpless%20cry%2C%20%E2%80%98What%20have%20I%20turned%20into%3F%E2%80%99%2C%20has%20become%20everybody%E2%80%99s%20agonised%20cry%20across%20nations.%20What%20is%20Muslimhood%3F%20What%20is%20being%20a%20Christian%3F%20What%20is%20being%20a%20female%3F%20What%20is%20being%20a%20Sanatani%20Hindu%2C%20or%20a%20non-Sanatani%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20similarly%20fascinating%20to%20read%20two%20great%20satirists%20in%20Hindi%20from%20the%201990s%3A%20Hari%20Shankar%20Parsai%20and%20Sharad%20Joshi.%20Is%20it%20a%20coincidence%20that%20like%20Kafka%20and%20Hasek%2C%20both%20hailed%20from%20the%20bowels%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20the%20central%20state%20in%20India%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20media%20brouhaha%20over%20our%20recent%20Moon%20Mission%20led%20one%20to%20re-read%20Parsai%E2%80%99s%20immortal%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindikunj.com%2F2022%2F02%2Finspector-matadeen-chand-par-harishankar-parsai.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EInspector%20Matadin%20Chaand%20Per%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20(Inspector%20Matadin%20on%20the%20moon).%20The%20story%20fantasises%20about%20an%20archetypal%20small%20town%20middle-level%20police%20inspector%2C%20Matadin%2C%20landing%20on%20the%20Moon%20as%20advisor%20to%20the%20Moon%20government%2C%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20Government%20of%20India.%20The%20Moon%20government%2C%20keen%20to%20modernise%20its%20law%20and%20order%20machinery%2C%20sends%20a%20Chandrayaan%20to%20India%20with%20a%20formal%20request%20for%20advice%20and%20assistance%20on%20how%20to%20set%20up%20a%20sound%20infrastructure%2C%20create%20codes%20of%20conduct%20and%20SOPs%20for%20their%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMatadin%20is%20sent%20because%20the%20bureaucracy%20in%20Delhi%20feels%20that%20since%20the%20Moon%20is%20a%20smaller%20planet%2C%20instead%20of%20the%20Inspector%20General%20of%20Police%2C%20a%20middle-level%20functionary%20with%20a%20reputation%20for%20getting%20work%20done%20should%20do.%20What%20follows%20the%20arrival%20of%20a%20crusty%20old%20police%20inspector%20from%20a%20small%20town%20is%20at%20once%20chaotic%20and%20hilarious.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWithin%20a%20few%20weeks%2C%20the%20incorruptible%2C%20mild%20and%20democratic%20police%20force%20in%20the%20Moon%20is%20transformed%20By%20%E2%80%98Pector%20Sa%E2%80%99%20Matadin%20ji%2C%20into%20a%20corrupt%2C%20muscular%20bureaucratic%20machine%20that%20learns%20how%20to%20maintain%20%E2%80%98crime%20registries%E2%80%99%20and%20bypass%20laws%20in%20the%20process%20to%20show%20most%20cases%20as%20%E2%80%9Csolved%E2%80%9D.%20These%20%E2%80%9Cresults%E2%80%9D%20are%20achieved%20with%20some%20help%20from%20a%20posse%20of%20false%20witnesses%2C%20trained%20by%20Inspector%20Matadin%20to%20lie%2C%20cheat%20and%20hoodwink%20the%20courts%20and%20get%20the%20so-called%20culprit%20silenced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELooking%20at%20the%20chaos%20and%20public%20disruptions%20the%20earthly%20training%20course%20causes%2C%20the%20hapless%20government%20finally%20requests%20that%20Inspector%20Matadin%20be%20called%20back.%20So%20one%20day%20Inspector%20Matadin%20leaves%20with%20his%20trainees%2C%20who%20openly%20weep%20and%20touch%20his%20feet%2C%20carrying%20some%20awards%20and%20a%20porous%20piece%20of%20moon%20rock%2C%20which%20the%20Inspector%20General%E2%80%99s%20wife%20had%20asked%20him%20to%20bring%20for%20her%20to%20scrub%20her%20heels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharad%20Joshi%20has%20created%20a%20similar%20gallery%20of%20such%20bureaucratese%20spouting%20rogues%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pustak.org%2Findex.php%2Fbooks%2Fbookdetails%2F6839%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EJeep%20Par%20Sawar%20Illiyan%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20(Maggots%20riding%20a%20government%20jeep)%2C%3Cem%3E%20Jaadu%20Ki%20Sarkar%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20tele%20serials%20like%20%E2%80%98Yeh%20Jo%20Hai%20Zindagi%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98Vikram%20Aur%20Betal%E2%80%99.%20It%20is%20interesting%20that%20the%20memorable%20ruffians%2C%20buffoons%20and%20corrupt%20bureaucratic%20bullies%20the%20two%20have%20created%20are%20flat%20characters%2C%20with%20smudged%20pasts%20and%20no%20memorable%20families.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%2C%20thus%2C%20become%20an%20every%20man%E2%80%99s%20experience%20of%20the%20bureaucratic%20and%20political%20power%20systems%20our%20times%20have%20created.%20Both%20satirists%20reject%20the%20road%20taken%20by%20those%20silky%20sentimental%20or%20psychologically%20obsessive%20popular%20novels.%20Their%20work%20with%20its%20ironic%20reading%20of%20the%20Indian%20democracy%2C%20seem%20much%20more%20relevant%20and%20readable%20in%20these%20absurd%20times%20because%20they%20carry%20a%20foreboding%20about%20the%20dark%20face%20of%20totalitarianism%2C%20about%20what%20is%20unsaid%20in%20democratic%20politics%20that%20floats%20all%20around%20us%20as%20unconfirmed%20whispers%2C%20and%20sudden%20bursts%20of%20sheer%20violence%20against%20the%20weak%2C%20which%20is%20never%20reported%20officially%2C%20and%20the%20reported%20versions%20of%20incidents.%20As%20the%20ghostly%20Betal%20of%20Joshi%20tells%20Vikram%2C%20%E2%80%98I%20am%20truth%20and%20you%20will%20never%20be%20able%20to%20control%20me!%E2%80%99%20(%3Cem%3EVikram%2C%20Main%20tere%20bus%20mein%20aaney%20wala%20nahin%3C%2Fem%3E.)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20very%20hard%20to%20slot%20subversive%20literature%20produced%20under%20any%20stressful%20and%20controlling%20regime.%20You%20can%20not%20call%20them%20purely%20political%20nor%20describe%20them%20as%20carrying%20a%20certain%20ideological%20orientation.%20In%20content%20and%20form%2C%20works%20like%20%3Cem%3ERet%20Samadhi%3C%2Fem%3E%20or%20%3Cem%3ERaag%20Darbari%3C%2Fem%3E%20have%20simply%20arisen%20from%20the%20world%20of%20literature%20as%20a%20revolt%20against%20a%20controlling%20regime.%20In%20the%20better%20writings%2C%20(yes%2C%20there%20is%20plenty%20of%20bad%20writing%20too%20that%20is%20far%20more%20acceptable%20officially)%20behind%20the%20hilarity%2C%20one%20also%20senses%20an%20anxiety%20about%20the%20State%20bulldozing%20all%20protective%20barriers%20around%20civilised%20democracies%20and%20the%20freedoms%20of%20all%20its%20citizens%20cutting%20across%20race%2C%20gender%2C%20caste%20and%20class.%20This%20is%20when%20the%20arts%20close%20ranks%20as%20an%20antidote%20to%20classical%20arts%2C%20stamped%20with%20politically%20correct%20religiosity%20that%20leaves%20humans%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThus%2C%20in%20music%2C%20we%20notice%20a%20sudden%20surge%20of%20public%20interest%20in%20what%20was%20seen%20as%20the%20concrete%20and%20the%20plebeian.%20The%20revival%20of%20interest%20in%20Punjabi%20and%20Bhojpuri%20folk%20music%20and%20Nirgun%20and%20Sufi%20poetry%20came%20out%20of%20music%20saying%20%E2%80%98no%E2%80%99%20to%20a%20suffocating%20feudalism.%20The%20father%20of%20the%20current%20change%2C%20vocalist%20Kumar%20Gandharva%2C%20set%20about%20defying%20classical%20gharana%20music%20with%20its%20obsolete%20regulations%20and%20made%20it%20free%20and%20available%20to%20all.%20He%20reconnected%20music%20to%20poetry%20and%20lent%20it%20an%20entirely%20new%20shape%20using%20folk%20music%20as%20the%20lode%20star.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20one%E2%80%99s%20bleakest%20moments%2C%20immersion%20in%20the%20constructive%20revolt%20by%20great%20art%20can%20still%20restore%20one%E2%80%99s%20faith%20in%20the%20unputdownable%20vitality%20of%20our%20great%20democracy.%20It%20was%20entirely%20befitting%20that%20when%20Kumar%20ji%2C%20one%20of%20the%20greatest%20musical%20innovators%20of%20our%20times%2C%20was%20being%20cremated%20in%20Devas%2C%20there%20were%20no%20State%20bugles%20nor%20smart%20battalions%20saluting%20the%20departed%20one.%20His%20lifelong%20cronies%2C%20the%20wandering%20Nirguni%20singers%2C%20stood%20with%20their%20simple%20Iktaras%20and%20sang%20%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20birds%20from%20afar%20Baba%2F%20we%20sing%20without%20mouths%2Fwe%20fly%20without%20wings%2C%20we%20can%20walk%20without%20feet.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693720465000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F03111839%2Fimage-1271.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fthe-arts%2Fthe-crafty-defiance-of-great-art%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Universally%2C%20writers%2C%20through%20their%20personal%20and%20collective%20experiences%2C%20often%20refrain%20from%20waving%20flags%2C%20worshipping%20at%20the%20grand%20statues%20of%20history%20and%20eulogizing%20the%20benevolence%20and%20divine%20stature%20of%20mortal%20regimes.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fthe-arts%2Fthe-crafty-defiance-of-great-art%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Babil%20defends%20Ranveer%20replacing%20SRK%20in%20Don%203%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693720029000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-103321753%2Cimgsize-30836.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fbabil-khan-defends-ranveer-singh-replacing-shah-rukh-khan-in-don-3-says-the-gully-boy-actor-will-shine-through%2Farticleshow%2F103321791.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F103321791.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EBabil%20Khan%20recently%20opened%20up%20about%20the%20controversy%20over%20Ranveer%20Singh%20replacing%20Shah%20Rukh%20Khan%20in%20Farhan%20Akhtar's%20Don%203.%20The%20young%20actor%20said%20that%20when%20you%20get%20a%20lot%20of%20hatred%20and%20you%20win%20through%20that%2C%20then%20the%20love%20is%20also%20at%20that%20level.%