22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.optimaacademy.online%2Fonline-elementary-school%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20Optima's%20website.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOptima%20Academy%20offers%20about%20250%20custom%20virtual%20environments%2C%20and%20also%20sells%20access%20to%20these%20environments%20to%20other%20independent%20schools%2C%20The%20New%20Yorker%20reported.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20one%20episode%20recounted%20in%20the%20report%2C%20students%20in%20a%20sixth%20grade%20science%20class%20were%20taken%20on%20a%20virtual%20field%20trip%20to%20a%20Everest%20base%20camp.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20virtual%20environment%20was%20%26quot%3Belaborately%20staged%26quot%3B%20with%20gray%20tents%2C%20sleeping%20bags%2C%20and%20sounds%20of%20wind%20in%20the%20background%2C%20the%20trip%20didn't%20go%20as%20planned%2C%20the%20New%20Yorker%20reported.%20The%20students%20struggled%20with%20the%20lesson%2C%20and%20had%20difficulties%20coordinating%20with%20each%20other%20through%20various%20activities.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EResearch%20also%20shows%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvirtual-reality-vr-side-effects-2018-3%5C%22%3EVR%20headsets%20can%20cause%20%26quot%3Bsimulator%20sickness%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3Bcybersickness%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20similar%20to%20motion%20sickness.%20Studies%20have%20also%20shown%20that%20prolonged%20periods%20of%20VR%20use%20could%20even%20result%20in%20%26quot%3Breality%20blurring%2C%26quot%3B%20where%20users%20have%20trouble%20distinguishing%20between%20virtual%20reality%20and%20real%20life%2C%20Jeremy%20Bailenson%2C%20the%20director%20of%20Stanford's%20Virtual%20Human%20Interaction%20Lab%2C%20told%20The%20New%20Yorker.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20founders%20suggest%20that%20school%20shouldn't%20be%20a%20student's%20whole%20life%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20drawbacks%20of%20virtual%20learning%20%E2%80%94%20and%20%3Ca%20hr