e%20party%2C%20citing%20financial%20problems%20and%20an%20apparent%20lack%20of%20trust.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20speaking%20with%20roughly%2020%20Democratic%20figures%20throughout%20the%20state%2C%20many%20told%20the%20outlet%20of%20their%20deep%20frustration%20at%20how%20the%20party%20%E2%80%94%20in%20one%20of%20the%20top%20presidential%20swing%20states%20in%20the%20country%20%E2%80%94%20is%20being%20run.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20state%20Democratic%20committee%20member%20described%20the%20state%20party%20as%20%26quot%3Bamateur%20hour.%26quot%3B%20And%20one%20former%20state%20party%20staffer%20called%20the%20organization%20a%20%26quot%3Bfucking%20disaster.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPolitico%20reported%20that%20the%20party%20went%20through%20some%20staff%20layoffs%20in%20July%2C%20and%20one%20of%20the%20party's%20political%20action%20committees%20reported%20only%20%247%2C500%20in%20its%20coffers%20as%20of%20June.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20Democrats%20have%20increasingly%20expressed%20concerns%20about%20the%20party%2C%20many%20are%20looking%20to%20the%20party%20chair%2C%20state%20Sen.%20Sharif%20Street%20of%20Philadelphia%2C%20to%20provide%20answers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20they're%20looking%20to%20help%20right%20the%20ship%20quickly%2C%20as%20a%20key%20state%20Supreme%20Court%20race%20will%20be%20held%20this%20November.%20The%20party%20has%20sought%20to%20make%20the%20contest%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwhyy.org%2Farticles%2Fpa-2023-elections-supreme-court-majority-mccaffery-carluccio-abortion-rights%2F%5C%22%3Ereferendum%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20abortion%20rights%20in%20the%20Keystone%20State.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Csection%20data-content-section%3D%5C%224%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20data-content-child-index%3D%5C%220-5%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20concerning%20that%20the%20state%20party%20is%20laying%20people%20off%20as%20we're%20heading%20into%20a%20really%20important%20Supreme%20Court%20race%2C%20which%20then%20leads%20into%20the%20presidential%20year%2C%26quot%3B%20Democratic%20consultant%20Mike%20Mikus%20told%20Politico.%20%26quot%3BThey're%20going%20to%20have%20to%20figure%20out%20a%20path%20forward%20to%20build%20their%20own%20fundraising%20operation%2C%20and%20it%20sounds%20like%20there's%20a%20lot%20of%20building%20to%20be%20done%20right%20now.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20data-content-child-index%3D%5C%220-5%5C%22%3EStreet%2C%20the%20party%20chair%2C%20told%20Politico%20that%20the%20state%20committee%20wasn't%20experiencing%20financial%20issues%20and%20touted%20funding%20that%20had%20already%20been%20used%20to%20hire%2020%20organizers.%20He%20also%20said%20that%20the%20state%20party's%20federal%20political%20action%20committee%20now%20had%20a%20balance%20of%20%24200%2C000.%20And%20he%20added%20that%20he%20had%20to%20push%20through%20layoffs%20due%20to%20high%20staff%20overhead%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20data-content-child-index%3D%5C%220-4%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BI%20really%20should%20have%20done%20some%20of%20that%20trimming%20back%20last%20December%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20of%20the%20layoffs.%20%26quot%3BBut%20they%20were%20people%20who%20had%20won%20so%20many%20elections.%20We%20have%20done%20things%20no%20other%20party%20did.%20And%20I%20couldn't%20look%20at%20any%20of%20them%20in%20the%20face%20and%20say%20I%20wanted%20to%20let%20them%20go.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20data-content-child-index%3D%5C%220-2%5C%22%3ESome%20Democrats%20remain%20concerned%20over%20the%20pace%20of%20fundraising%2C%20especially%20as%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20and%20Senator%20Bob%20Casey%20Jr.%20are%20both%20aiming%20to%20continue%20the%20party's%20success%20next%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20data-content-child-index%3D%5C%220-2%5C%22%3EStreet%20told%20Politico%20that%20he%20has%20sought%20to%20bring%20on%20organizers%20from%20Pennsylvania%2C%20which%20has%20caused%20some%20friction%20with%20national%20Democratic%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20data-content-child-index%3D%5C%220-2%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20done%20things%20a%20little%20differently%2C%20and%20I%20know%20that%20may%20have%20ruffled