0that%20it%20%E2%80%9Cmaintains%20the%20highest%20standards%20of%20professionalism%20and%20functions%20squarely%20within%20the%20ambit%20of%20the%20law%E2%80%9D.%20The%20BBC%20report%20uses%20%E2%80%9Cquotes%20of%20unidentified%20journalists%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cwithout%20particulars%20of%20date%20and%20place%E2%80%9D%20to%20%E2%80%9Cbolster%20..%20non-existent%20claims%20of%20state%20overreach%20against%20journalists%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20Police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CJ%26amp%3BK%20Police%20condemns%20the%20attempt%20of%20a%20media%20house%20such%20as%20the%20BBC%20to%20misrepresent%20the%20conditions%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%20in%20which%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20Police%20has%20stood%20firmly%20on%20the%20front%20lines%20in%20the%20war%20against%20terror%20and%20lost%20thousands%20of%20its%20bravest%20men%20in%20an%20attempt%20to%20safeguard%20the%20people%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20national%20and%20international%20media%20organisations%2C%20including%20the%20Paris-based%20press%20freedom%20watchdog%20Reporters%20Sans%20Frontiers%20(RSF)%20and%20the%20New%20York-headquartered%20Committee%20to%20Protect%20Journalists%2C%20have%20flagged%20the%20deterioration%20of%20press%20freedom%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20calling%20upon%20authorities%20to%20release%20the%20four%20journalists%20incarcerated%20in%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20slipped%2011%20ranks%20further%20to%20161%20out%20of%20180%20countries%20in%20terms%20of%20press%20freedom%20according%20to%20the%20RSF%E2%80%99s%20Press%20Freedom%20Index-2023%20with%20the%20organisation%20stating%20that%20the%20situation%20for%20journalists%20was%20%E2%80%9Cvery%20serious%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693663030000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F06%2F06111908%2FPress-freedom.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fjammu-kashmir-police-b