ular%20hospital%20checkups.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJamkholal%20Touthang%20used%20to%20visit%20Shija%20Hospital%20every%20alternate%20day%20for%20kidney%20dialysis%2C%20but%20is%20now%20wondering%20what%20to%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMore%20than%2050%20state%20and%20central%20forces%20came%20and%20clearly%20told%20us%20that%20they%20are%20merely%20following%20orders%20from%20the%20Union%20home%20ministry%2C%E2%80%9D%20Jamkholal%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20asked%20a%20number%20of%20thus%20evacuated%20Kuki%20citizens%20if%20they%20had%20asked%20officials%20to%20show%20them%20the%20order%20from%20the%20Union%20home%20ministry.%20Most%20said%20they%20were%20afraid.%20The%20security%20forces%20gave%20them%20less%20than%20an%20hour%20to%20pack%20all%20their%20belongings%20and%20they%20were%20asked%20to%20sit%20in%20vehicles%20without%20asking%20any%20questions%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMang%2C%20one%20of%20the%20Kuki%20residents%20who%20had%20been%20living%20in%20Imphal%E2%80%99s%20New%20Lambulane%20and%20has%20now%20been%20evacuated%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CRight%20now%2C%20we%E2%80%99re%20at%20a%20relief%20camp%20in%20Motbung%20outside%20Imphal.%20We%20are%20Indian%20citizens%2C%20but%20the%20government%20of%20India%20cannot%20provide%20us%20with%20protection%20to%20live%20in%20our%20own%20houses%3F%20It%20is%20the%20failure%20of%20the%20Indian%20government.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fsurviving-without-pay-unable-to-venture-out-the-life-of-kuki-families-since-the-manipur-violence%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Surviving%20Without%20Pay%2C%20Unable%20to%20Venture%20Out%E2%80%99%3A%20How%20Kuki%20Families%20Are%20Navigating%20Life%20in%20Imphal%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20them%20left%20without%20any%20money.%20Mang%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CMost%20of%20us%20left%20in%20a%20hurry%2C%20so%20no%20one%20was%20able%20to%20take%20money.%20We%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20how%20we%20will%20manage%20in%20the%20coming%20days.%20My%20passport%20and%20Aadhaar%20are%20still%20at%20my%20place.%20I%20am%20fearing%20that%20sooner%20or%20later%2C%20our%20houses%20will%20also%20be%20burnt%20down.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20situation%20in%20Manipur%20%E2%80%93%20roiled%20by%20ethnic%20violence%20since%20May%202%20%E2%80%93%20had%20been%20particularly%20tense%20since%20August%2029.%20As%20many%20as%20eight%20people%20have%20died%20since%20then%20individuals.%20Earlier%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E%20had%20reported%20that%20a%20few%20families%20were%20still%20residing%20in%20Imphal%E2%80%99s%20New%20Lambulane%2C%20with%20the%20police%20providing%20them%20security.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20New%20Lambulane%20area%20is%20tightly%20populated.%20Outside%20the%20area%2C%20many%20Central%20and%20state%20forces%20had%20been%20deployed%20to%20guard%20the%20Kuki%20families%20living%20in%20the%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20also%20reached%20out%20to%20one%20of%20the%20Naga%20residents%20living%20in%20New%20Lambulane%2C%20who%20said%20later%20in%20the%20day%20on%20September%202%20that%C2%A0%20personnel%20of%20%E2%80%9CManipur%20Police%2C%20the%20CRPF%20and%20RAF%E2%80%9D%20were%20in%20the%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20place%20is%20still%20safe.%20I%E2%80%99m%20wondering%20why%20they%20had%20to%20be%20%E2%80%98forcefully%E2%80%99%20taken%20out%20from%20the%20area%2C%20especially%20at%202%3A30%20in%20the%20night%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20Naga%20resident%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%20The%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20also%20reached%20out%20to%20DGP%20Rajiv%20Singh%20but%20he%20refused%20to%20give%20a%20comment%20over%20phone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2024%20evacuated%20people%20have%20written%20a%20press%20release%20expressing%20their%20strong%20disapproval%20of%20this%20evacuation%2C%20emphasising%20%E2%80%9CIndia%E2%80%99s%20failure%20to%20ensure%20its%20citizens%E2%80%99%20safety%20in%20the%20face%20of%20disruptive%20forces.%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20August%2031%2C%20during%20crossfire%20and%20bombings%2C%20six%20people%20lost%20their%20lives%20%E2%80%93%20four%20from%20the%20Kuki%20community%20and%20two%20from%20the%20Meitei%20community%2C%20totalling%20eight%20casualties%20since%20August%2029.%20Both%20Bishnupur%20and%20Churachandpur%20districts%20experienced%20a%20complete%20shutdown%20for%20two%20days%20till%20September%201.%20The%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs%20also%20announced%20the%20deployment%20of%2050%20additional%20CRPF%20companies%20to%20strengthen%20buffer%20zones%20between%20the%20hills%20and%20the%20valley%20in%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoxing%20champion%20Mary%20Kom%20also%20wrote%20a%20letter%20to%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CSecurity%20forces%20should%20stop%20both%20communities%20from%20entering%20Kom%20villages%2C%20army%20should%20save%20Kom%20tribe.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20firing%20is%20ongoing%20near%20the%20valley%20villages%20of%20Naranseina%2C%20Thamnapokpi%2C%20and%20Ngangkha%20Leikai.%20On%20the%20hillside%2C%20there%20is%20firing%20near%20Kangathei%20and%20Khoirentak%20village.%20Kangathei%20is%20the%20birthplace%20of%20Mary%20Kom.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693660875000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F02184835%2Fsignal-2023-09-02-183143_002.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fmanipur-new-lambulances-last-kuki-families%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20total%20of%2024%20individuals%20from%20the%20Kuki%20community%2C%20including%20infants%20and%20people%20in%20need%20of%20regular%20hospital%20checkups%2C%20were%20taken%20from%20New%20Lambulane%20to%20a%20camp%20in%20a%20village.%20They%20said%20they%20were%20given%20little%20time%20to%20pack%20and%20fear%20their%20homes%20will%20now%20be%20destroyed.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22