Fstatus%2F1697503057444229220%5C%22%3Etold%3C%2Fa%3E%20reporters%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9COnce%20the%20committee%20comes%20up%20with%20a%20report%2C%20it%20will%20be%20placed%20in%20the%20public%20domain%20and%20a%20discussion%20will%20be%20held.%20When%20the%20report%20comes%20to%20parliament%2C%20it%20will%20be%20discussed%20in%20parliament%20as%20well.%20There%20is%20nothing%20to%20be%20nervous%20about%2C%20as%20discussions%20will%20be%20held.%20We%20are%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20largest%20democracy%20and%20we%20are%20known%20as%20the%20mother%20of%20democracy.%20This%20is%20the%20evolution%20of%20democracy%20in%20the%20mother%20of%20democracy%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20new%20issues%20that%20come%20in%20national%20interest%20need%20to%20be%20discussed%20in%20a%20democracy.%20This%20does%20not%20mean%20that%20such%20a%20system%20will%20be%20brought%20in%20tomorrow.%20We%20have%20not%20said%20that.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20was%20announced%20on%20September%202%2C%20that%20the%20government%20has%20formed%20an%20eight%3C%2Fspan%3E-member%20committee%20to%20examine%20the%20%E2%80%98One%20nation%2C%20One%20election%E2%80%99%20possibility.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20President%20Ram%20Nath%20Kovind%20was%20appointed%20as%20chairman%20of%20the%20committee.%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20Congress%20MP%20Adhir%20Ranjan%20Chowdhury%2C%20former%20Rajya%20Sabha%20LoP%20Ghulam%20Nabi%20Azad%2C%20former%20finance%20commission%20chairman%20N.K.%20Singh%2C%20former%20secretary%20general%20Lok%20Sabha%20Subhash%20C.%20Kashyap%2C%20senior%20advocate%20Harish%20Salve%20and%20former%20chief%20vigilance%20commissioner%20Sanjay%20Kothari%20are%20in%20the%20committee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20notification%20added%20that%20law%20minister%20Arjun%20Ram%20Meghwal%20will%20attend%20the%20committee%20meetings%20as%20a%20special%20invitee.%20The%20committee%20is%20expected%20to%20begin%20functioning%20immediately%20and%20submit%20its%20recommendations%20%E2%80%9Cat%20the%20earliest%E2%80%9D.%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F01%2F25204736%2FScreen-Shot-2020-01-25-at-8.47.13-PM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221032%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F01%2F25204736%2FScreen-Shot-2020-01-25-at-8.47.13-PM.png%201032w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F01%2F25204736%2FScreen-Shot-2020-01-25-at-8.47.13-PM-300x166.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F01%2F25204736%2FScreen-Shot-2020-01-25-at-8.47.13-PM-1024x567.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-430096%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22571%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20president%20Ram%20Nath%20Kovind.%20Photo%3A%20PTI%3Cb%3E%E2%80%98One%20Nation%2C%20One%20Election%E2%80%99%20proposal%20not%20new%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20idea%20of%20simultaneous%20elections%20is%20not%20new.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20first%20few%20general%20elections%20post-independence%20were%20held%20simultaneously%2C%20with%20the%20state%20legislative%20assembly%20elections%2C%20according%20to%20a%20paper%20published%20by%20the%20Legal%20and%20Constitutional%20Affairs%20Wing%20of%20the%20Research%20%26amp%3B%20Information%20Division%2C%20Lok%20Sabha%20Secretariat.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20the%20practice%20continued%20till%201967%2C%20due%20to%20the%20premature%20dissolution%20of%20some%20state%20assemblies%20in%201968%20and%201969%2C%20the%20system%20of%20simultaneous%20elections%20was%20disrupted.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThus%2C%20since%20the%201967%20elections%2C%20the%20practice%20of%20simultaneous%20elections%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20the%20Vidhan%20Sabhas%20could%20not%20be%20maintained%20and%20the%20elections%20have%20still%20not%20been%20realigned%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20paper%20states.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EModi%20government%E2%80%99s%20three%20committees%20to%20study%20simultaneous%20polls%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESince%20the%20Modi%20government%20came%20to%20power%20in%202014%2C%20simultaneous%20elections%20have%20been%20on%20the%20agenda.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Modi%20government%20has%20already%20constituted%20three%20separate%20committees%20to%20look%20into%20the%20possibility%20of%20having%20a%20system%20for%20%E2%80%9COne%20Nation%2C%20One%20Polls.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ELaw%20Commission%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20August%202018%2C%20the%20Law%20Commission%20of%20India%20released%20its%20draft%20report%20on%20simultaneous%20elections.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fprsindia.org%2Fpolicy%2Freport-summaries%2Fdraft-report-simultaneous-elections%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EPRS%20Legislative%20Research%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20the%20Law%20Commission%20draft%20report%20noted%20that%20simultaneous%20elections%20cannot%20be%20held%20within%20the%20existing%20framework%20of%20the%20constitution.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20order%20to%20conduct%20such%20simultaneous%20elections%2C%20it%20said%20that%20there%20needs%20to%20be%20made%20appropriate%20amendments%20to%20the%20constitution%2C%20the%20Representation%20of%20the%20People%20Act%201951%2C%20and%20the%20Rules%20of%20Procedure%20of%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20state%20Assemblies.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20also%20said%20that%20at%20least%2050%25%20of%20the%20states%20should%20ratify%20the%20constitutional%20amendments.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20the%20Law%20Commission%20in%201999%20had%20suggested%20simultaneous%20elections.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Commission%20%E2%80%93%20then%20headed%20by%20former%20Justice%20B.P%20Jeevan%20Reddy%20%E2%80%93%20in%20its%20170th%20Report%20on%20Reform%20of%20Electoral%20Laws%20(1999)%20had%20cautioned%20that%20such%20elections%20cannot%20be%20held%20overnight.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20recommended%20advancing%20some%20state%20elections%2C%20and%20making%20adjustments%20in%20the%20schedule%20of%20others%2C%20a%20possible%20constitutional%20amendment%20for%20extending%20or%20curtailing%20the%20term%20of%20one%20or%20more%20legislative%20assemblies%2C%20and%20also%20suggested%20simultaneous%20motion%20of%20no-confidence%20in%20the%20incumbent%20government%20as%20well%20as%20confidence%20in%20alternative%20government%2C%20among%20others.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fsimultaneous-polls-democracy-india%5C%22%3ESimultaneous%20Polls%20Not%20the%20Panacea%20for%20the%20Ills%20Plaguing%20Indian%20Democracy%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EParliamentary%20standing%20committee%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20department-related%20Parliamentary%20Standing%20Committee%20on%20Personnel%2C%20Public%20Grievances%2C%20Law%20and%20Justice%2C%20Rajya%20Sabha%20in%20its%2079th%20report%20in%202015%20also%20studied%20the%20possibility%20of%20holding%20simultaneous%20elections.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETitled%20%E2%80%98Feasibility%20of%20Holding%20Simultaneous%20Elections%20to%20the%20House%20of%20People%20(Lok%20Sabha)%20and%20State%20Legislative%20Assemblies%E2%80%99%20the%20report%20was%20tabled%20in%20parliament%20on%20December%202015.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20report%20took%20into%20account%20the%20findings%20of%20the%201999%20Law%20Commission%20report%20and%20recommended%20holding%20simultaneous%20elections%20in%20two%20phases%20with%20elections%20of%20some%20assemblies%20at%20the%20midterm%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20the%20remaining%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20tenure%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20also%20recommended%20that%20early%20elections%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20or%20state%20assemblies%20can%20take%20place%20only%20if%20either%20of%20two%20conditions%20is%20met%3A%20i)%20a%20motion%20for%20an%20early%20General%20Election%20is%20agreed%20either%20by%20at%20least%20two-thirds%20of%20the%20whole%20House%20(including%20vacant%20seats)%3B%20or%20ii)%20If%20a%20no-confidence%20motion%20is%20passed%20and%20no%20alternative%20government%20is%20confirmed%20by%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20or%20State%20Legislative%20Assemblies%20within%20fourteen%20days%20by%20means.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ENITI%20Aayog%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20February%202018%2C%20minister%20of%20state%20for%20law%20and%20justice%20P.P.%20Chaudhary%20said%20in%20a%20written%20reply%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20that%20the%20government%20had%20received%20the%20recommendations%20of%20the%20NITI%20Aayog%20in%20a%20paper%20titled%20%E2%80%9CAnalysis%20of%20Simultaneous%20Elections%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EChaudhary%20said%20that%20the%20NITI%20Aayog%20report%20had%20taken%20into%20account%20the%20Standing%20Committee%E2%80%99s%20report%20and%20worked%20out%20a%20possible%20framework%20whereby%20elections%20to%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20state%20assemblies%20could%20be%20held%20simultaneously%20in%20two%20phases.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20paper%20envisages%20holding%20simultaneous%20elections%20to%20the%20Assemblies%20of%20about%20one%20half%20of%20the%20States%20along%20with%20Lok%20Sabha%20General%20Elections%20due%20in%20April-May%202019%20and%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20States%20in%20the%20mid-way%2C%20i.e.%20October-November%2C%202021%2C%20entailing%20extension%20or%20curtailment%20of%20the%20duration%20of%20the%20Assemblies%20wherever%20required%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20this%20would%20require%20amendments%20to%20the%20relevant%20provisions%20of%20the%20Constitution.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20government%20has%20not%20taken%20any%20decision%20on%20the%20recommendations%20of%20any%20of%20these%20committee%20reports%20and%20has%20now%20come%20up%20with%20a%20fourth%20committee%20to%20look%20into%20the%20subject%20of%20%E2%80%9COne%20Nation%2C%20One%20Election.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EModi%E2%80%99s%20pitch%20for%20%E2%80%98One%20Nation%2C%20One%20Election%E2%80%99%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EApart%20from%20these%20three%20committees%20that%20have%20studied%20the%20issue%2C%20over%20the%20years%2C%20Modi%20himself%20has%20strongly%20pitched%20for%20the%20idea%20of%20simultaneous%20elections.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20his%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Findependence-day-speech-narendra-modi-kashmir-370%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E2019%20Independence%20Day%20speech%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20Modi%20said%20after%20the%20government%20had%20achieved%20%E2%80%98one%20nation%2C%20one%20tax%E2%80%99%20through%20the%20Goods%20and%20Services%20Tax%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthere%20are%20now%20demands%20of%20%E2%80%98one%20nation%2C%20one%20election%E2%80%99%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20June%20of%20that%20year%2C%20soon%20after%20returning%20to%20power%2C%20Modi%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fall-party-meeting-one-nation-one-election-modi-opposition%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Emet%20leaders%20of%20various%20political%20parties%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3Eto%20explore%20the%20possibilities%20of%20simultaneous%20elections.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20November%202020%2C%20while%20addressing%20the%20All%20India%20Presiding%20Officers%2C%20Modi%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmodi-one-nation-one-election-single-voters-list%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esaid%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%99One%20Nation%2C%20One%20Election%E2%80%99%20isn%E2%80%99t%20just%20an%20issue%20of%20deliberation%20but%20also%20a%20need%20of%20the%20country.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20January%202022%2C%20Modi%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Fpm-modi-calls-for-higher-polling-discussion-on-one-nation-one-election%2Farticleshow%2F89113270.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereiterated%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20his%20call%20for%20simultaneous%20elections%20and%20said%20that%20continuous%20cycles%20of%20elections%20result%20in%20politics%20being%20seen%20in%20everything%20while%20development%20works%20suffer.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F25173947%2FScreenshot-2023-08-25-at-5.39.05-PM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F25173947%2FScreenshot-2023-08-25-at-5.39.05-PM.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F25173947%2FScreenshot-2023-08-25-at-5.39.05-PM-300x164.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F25173947%2FScreenshot-2023-08-25-at-5.39.05-PM-1024x560.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-669865%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22656%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20addresses%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%E2%80%99s%20Regional%20Panchayati%20Raj%20Council%20in%20West%20Bengal%20on%20August%2012%2C%202023.%20Photo%3A%20Screengrab%20via%20YouTube%2FNarendra%20Modi%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EThe%20challenge%20of%20simultaneous%20elections%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20a%20written%20reply%20to%20Lok%20Sabha%20in%20March%20this%20year%2C%20then-law%20minister%20Kiren%20Rijiju%20said%20that%20while%20the%20subject%20has%20been%20studied%20by%20the%20Parliamentary%20Standing%20Committee%2C%20and%20such%20elections%20%E2%80%9Cwould%20result%20in%20huge%20savings%20to%20the%20public%20exchequer%E2%80%9D%2C%20some%20challenges%20remain.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20included%2C%20%E2%80%9CBringing%20amendments%20in%20not%20less%20than%20five%20articles%20of%20Constitution%2C%20namely%2C%20article%2083%20relating%20to%20duration%20of%20Houses%20of%20Parliament%2C%20article%2085%20relating%20to%20dissolution%20of%20the%20House%20of%20the%20People%20by%20the%20President%2C%20article%20172%20relating%20to%20duration%20of%20the%20State%20Legislatures%2C%20article%20174%20relating%20to%20dissolution%20of%20the%20State%20Legislatures%20and%20article%20356%20relating%20to%20the%20imposition%20of%20President%E2%80%99s%20Rule%20in%20the%20States.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20also%20said%20that%20the%20consensus%20of%20all%20political%20parties%20and%20state%20governments%C2%A0would%20be%20essential%20with%20regard%20to%20India%E2%80%99s%20federal%20structure%20of%20governance.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERijiju%20added%20that%20the%20exercise%20would%20also%20need%20an%20additional%20number%20of%20EVMs%2FVVPATs%2C%20which%20would%20cost%20a%20huge%20amount%2C%20%E2%80%9Cmight%20be%20in%20thousands%20of%20crores%E2%80%9D%20along%20with%20additional%20polling%20personnel%20and%20security%20forces.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20former%20chief%20election%20commissioner%20T.S.%20Krishna%20Murthy%20said%20while%20simultaneous%20elections%20may%20provide%20more%20advantages%20than%20disadvantages%2C%20implementation%20remains%20the%20key%20question.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20has%20certain%20advantages%20and%20disadvantages%2C%20maybe%20the%20advantages%20are%20more.%20But%20the%20question%20is%20implementation.%20What%20is%20most%20crucial%20is%20the%20constitutional%20amendment%2C%20unless%20that%20is%20possible%20it%20will%20remain%20a%20discussion%20on%20paper.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20advantage%20is%20that%20you%20save%20money%2C%20the%20disadvantage%20is%20that%20state%20elections%20will%20be%20affected%20%5Bby%20the%20mood%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%5D.%20But%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20agree%20with%20that%20as%20state%20elections%20have%20been%20held%20parallelly%20to%20general%20elections%20and%20states%20like%20Odisha%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20and%20Kerala%2C%20have%20had%20different%20parties%20elected.%20But%20these%20are%20the%20questions%20being%20raised%20by%20opposition%20parties.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E%E2%80%98Diversionary%2C%20tactical%20move%E2%80%99%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOpposition%20parties%20meanwhile%20have%20opposed%20the%20move%20to%20bring%20about%20simultaneous%20elections.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnshul%20Avijit%2C%20national%20spokesperson%20of%20the%20Congress%2C%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Ethat%20the%20Modi%20government%20is%20using%20the%20idea%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cdiversionary%20and%20tactical%20move.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20two%20aspects.%20It%20is%20a%20diversionary%20and%20a%20tactical%20move%20to%20bring%20nationalism%20to%20local%20issues%20and%20therefore%20influence%20voters.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20not%20to%20simplify%20the%20electoral%20process.%20It%20is%20basically%20to%20grab%20power%20in%20a%20manner%20that%20has%20eluded%20them%20so%20far%20because%20they%20have%20been%20far%20more%20unsuccessful%20in%20winning%20state%20elections.%20So%20they%20are%20thinking%20of%20a%20way%20to%20amend%20the%20constitution%20through%20brute%20force%20and%20grabbing%20power%2C%E2%80%9D%20Avijit%20said%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20added%20that%20while%20the%20idea%20is%20not%20new%2C%20it%20is%20being%20brought%20up%20now%20because%20Modi%20is%20%E2%80%9Cfacing%20challenges%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWhenever%20there%20is%20a%20serious%20challenge%20to%20the%20prime%20minister%20%E2%80%93%20like%20the%20meeting%20of%20the%20INDIA%20parties%2C%20or%20allegations%20against%20Adani%2C%20or%20China%20releasing%20a%20map%20in%20which%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%20is%20included%2C%20or%20unemployment%2C%20widespread%20poverty%2C%20or%20bringing%20Manipur%20under%20control%20%E2%80%93%20the%20prime%20minister%20comes%20up%20with%20something%20like%20this.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOther%20members%20of%20the%20opposition%20alliance%2C%20INDIA%2C%20also%20said%20that%20the%20Modi%20government%20is%20using%20the%20idea%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAamAadmiParty%2Fstatus%2F1697541991460917286%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9Cmislead%20the%20country%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20as%20the%20third%20meeting%20of%20the%20bloc%20was%20underway%20in%20Mumbai.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fsimultaneous-elections-centralisation-power%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Simultaneous%20Elections%E2%80%99%20or%20Centralisation%20of%20Power%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EBJP%20calls%20it%20a%C2%A0%20%E2%80%9Cwelcome%20move%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20welcomed%20the%20move.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20a%20positive%20development%20that%20has%20been%20initiated%20by%20the%20party%20and%20the%20government%20and%20it%20should%20be%20welcomed%2C%E2%80%9D%20Syed%20Zafar%20Islam%2C%20national%20spokesperson%20of%20the%20BJP%2C%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20committee%20has%20been%20entrusted%20to%20discuss%20the%20advantages%20and%20disadvantages%20(of%20simultaneous%20polls)%20and%20it%20will%20evaluate%20every%20possibility%20and%20submit%20its%20report%20on%20the%20floor%20of%20the%20parliament.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20latest%20move%20to%20form%20the%20committee%20comes%20a%20day%20after%20speculation%20surrounding%20Joshi%E2%80%99s%20announcement%20of%20a%20special%20session%20of%20parliament%20scheduled%20to%20be%20held%20next%20month%20from%20September%2018-22.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20has%20remained%20tightlipped%20about%20the%20agenda%20of%20the%20special%20session.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20parliamentary%20affairs%20minister%20has%20very%20clearly%20stated%20that%20the%20special%20session%20has%20been%20convened%20to%20consider%20issues%20that%20will%20help%20the%20progress%20of%20the%20nation.%20All%20the%20important%20issues%20will%20be%20discussed%20on%20the%20floor%20of%20the%20parliament%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Islam.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENote%3A%20This%20article%20has%20been%20updated%20with%20news%20on%20the%20committee%E2%80%99s%20notification.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693642302000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F01%2F21203422%2Fevm-hacking-pti.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fone-nation-one-election-fourth-committee%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20Congress%20MP%20Adhir%20Ranjan%20Chowdhury%2C%20former%20Rajya%20Sabha%20LoP%20Ghulam%20Nabi%20Azad%2C%20and%20others%20have%20now%20been%20appointed%20as%20members%20of%20the%20Committee.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A31%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fone-nation-one-election-fourth-committee%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Assam%20Rifles%20DG%20Says%20Manipur%20Situation%20Unprecedented%2C%20'Never%20Faced%20Anything%20of%20This%20Kind'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F02122538%2FScreenshot-2023-09-02-at-12.25.06-PM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20In%20comments%20that%20underline%20the%20seriousness%20of%20the%20ongoing%20violence%20in%20the%20sensitive%20border%20state%20of%20Manipur%2C%20the%20director%20general%20of%20Assam%20Rifles%2C%20Lt%20General%20P.C.%20Nair%2C%20on%20Friday%2C%20September%201%2C%20said%20that%20the%20situation%20in%20Manipur%20was%20unprecedented.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20situation%20that%20we%20are%20facing%20in%20Manipur%20is%20unprecedented.%20We%20have%20never%20faced%20anything%20of%20this%20kind%20in%20history.%20It%20is%20new%20to%20us%2C%20it%20is%20new%20to%20Manipur%20too.%20Something%20similar%20happened%20in%20the%20early%2090s%20when%20the%20Nagas%20and%20Kukis%20fought%20and%20then%20within%20the%20Kuki%20groups%20also%20there%20was%20a%20fight%20in%20the%20late%2090s%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fmanipur-violence-assam-rifles-dg-pc-nair-meitei-kuki-ethnic-clashes-101693540206846.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ELt%20General%20Nair%20told%20ANI%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20The%20statement%20is%20significant%20and%20alarming%20as%20it%20comes%20from%20the%20Assam%20Rifles%20and%20is%20not%20referring%20to%20an%20insurgency%20but%20to%20the%20ethnic%20clashes%20between%20the%20Meiteis%20and%20Kukis.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F8C37Ps2fDm0%3Fsi%3DI0p80djLqm2WI76y%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20violence%20in%20Manipur%20has%20so%20far%20caused%20at%20least%20160%20deaths%20and%20there%20are%20reports%20of%202%2C000%20villages%20being%20burnt%20and%20over%20360%20churches%20either%20being%20burnt%20or%20destroyed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELt%20General%20Nair%20spoke%20of%20the%20multiple%20challenges%20that%20the%20armed%20forces%20were%20facing%20in%20the%20state%20that%20has%20been%20marred%20by%20very%20serious%20violence%20since%20May%203.%20Lt%20General%20Nair%20said%20the%20%E2%80%9Clarge%20number%20of%20weapons%E2%80%9D%20with%20civilians%20was%20a%20key%20concern.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20society%20has%20become%20weaponised.%20Unless%20these%20weapons%20come%20back%20in%20whatever%20way%20they%20can%2C%20this%20challenge%20will%20be%20the%20biggest.%20Today%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20so%20much%20against%20each%20other%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20so%20corrupted.%20This%20needs%20to%20be%20stalled%2C%E2%80%9D%20were%20his%20exact%20words.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fmanipur-looted-weaponry-yet-to-return-to-police-armouries-cm-appeals-afresh-for-surrender%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20had%20reported%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20how%20various%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eestimates%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20had%20put%20the%20weapons%20%E2%80%9Clooted%E2%80%9D%20from%20police%20armouries%20at%20more%20than%203%2C000.%20On%20June%203%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2F140-weapons-surrendered-manipur-amit-shah-8642463%2F%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20as%20many%20as%204%2C000%20weapons%20had%20been%20looted%20from%20the%20police%20and%20state%20armoury.%20It%20also%20said%20that%20till%20then%20only%20650%20weapons%20had%20been%20recovered.%20The%20kind%20of%20weapons%20%E2%80%9Clooted%E2%80%9D%20is%20a%20grave%20concern.%20FIRs%20seen%20by%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20indicate%20the%20loot%20of%20sophisticated%20weapons%20like%20AK%20and%20INSAS%20rifles%2C%20and%20bombs%2C%20among%20others.%20Looters%20also%20took%20away%20bulletproof%20jackets%20and%20set%20fire%20to%20police%20stations.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EManipur%20is%20meant%20to%20enjoy%20an%20advantage%20as%20per%20the%20ruling%20BJP%2C%20of%20a%20%E2%80%9Cdouble-engine%E2%80%9D%20government%2C%20with%20the%20same%20party%20in%20control%20in%20Imphal%20and%20in%20Delhi.%20But%20despite%20a%20long%20and%20unprecedented%20visit%20and%20stay%20by%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20the%20violence%20is%20not%20under%20control.%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20last%20month%2C%20upon%20summoning%20the%20chief%20secretary%20of%20the%20state%20had%20remarked%2C%20that%20there%20was%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fbreakdown-of-law-order-supreme-court-manipur-video-case-8871282%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eno%20law%20and%20order%20left%20in%20Manipur%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9C.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20role%20of%20the%20state%20police%2C%20whether%20in%20controlling%20violence%20or%20in%20allowing%20the%20%E2%80%9Clooting%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20armouries%2C%20has%20been%20pointed%20out%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20and%20cases%20of%20violence%20have%20been%20shifted%20out%20of%20the%20state%20to%20courts%20in%20Assam.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMeanwhile%2C%20fresh%20violence%20has%20killed%20at%20least%20eight%20persons%20in%20the%20districts%20of%20Bishnupur%20and%20Churachandpur%20over%20the%20last%20three%20days%20with%20firing%20and%20violence%20continuing%20since%20August%2029.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20is%20little%20coordination%20between%20central%20forces%20and%20those%20from%20the%20state.%20Assam%20Rifles%20has%20been%20locked%20in%20another%20unprecedented%20conflict%20with%20the%20state%20police.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fmanipur-police-files-fir-against-assam-rifles-for-allowing-kuki-militants-to-flee%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EManipur%20Police%20filed%20an%20FIR%20against%20Assam%20Rifles%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20last%20month%20for%20%E2%80%9Callowing%20Kuki%20Militants%20to%20flee%E2%80%9D.%20A%20video%20of%20a%20heated%20exchange%20between%20Assam%20Rifles%20and%20Bishnupur%20police%20had%20earlier%20gone%20viral.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAssam%20Rifles%20is%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Fopinion%2Fdangerous-wedge-the-assam-rifles-humiliation-in-manipur%2Fcid%2F1961116%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eadministratively%20under%20the%20Union%20home%20ministry%20but%20operationally%20works%20under%20the%20army.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20It%20is%20commanded%20by%20army%20officers%2C%20who%20constitute%20around%2080%25%20of%20the%20officer%20cadre.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693638608000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F02122538%2FScreenshot-2023-09-02-at-12.25.06-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fassam-rifles-dg-manipur-situation-unprecedented%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Lt%20General%20P.C.%20Nair%20flagged%20the%20%E2%80%9Clarge%20